    # n "Even as weird and humiliating and... and scary as it was for me this afternoon..."
    n "Por más raro y humillante y... aterrador que haya sido lo de esta tarde... "

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:395
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_0ac9b42c:

    # n neutral_side "Once the dust settled, I couldn't help but feel how much it thrilled me to experience that kind of powerlessness." with dissolve
    n neutral_side "Cuando el polvo de dispersó, no pude evitar darme cuenta de lo emocionante que fue experimentar esa clase de impotencia." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:343
