    # n irritated "No, I don't mean like last time." with dissolve
    n irritated "No, no como la última vez." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:355
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_01e3a91e:

    # n sleep "We wouldn't be pretending I'm a captured settler, or some petty thief who needed a lesson." with dissolve
    n sleep "No estaríamos fingiendo que soy una colona secuestrada, o una ladronzuela que necesitaba una lección." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:356
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_182b9bfb:

    # n sigh "I don't mean roleplay, Kyou." with dissolve
    n sigh "No hablo de juegos de rol, Kyou." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:357
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_4f20819b:

    # n concerned "I want you to dominate... me!" with dissolve
    n concerned "Quiero que me domines... ¡a mí!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:358
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_4111f097:

    # n sigh "I want to be aware of you trying to command me to do and think things. I want to try and resist, and... I want to succumb." with dissolve
    n sigh "Quiero intentar resistir, y... y quiero sucumbir." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:359
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_ac91ad4b:

    # "I... It's not like I didn't know this was coming."
    "Yo... No es como si no hubiera sabido que esto vendría."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:413
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_0c7a39f2:

    # n sleepy "You're not surprised, are you? We've already come this far." with dissolve
    n sleepy "No estás sorprendido, ¿o sí? Ya hemos llegado tan lejos." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:361
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_0741298c:

    # "Everything we've been doing has led to this moment."
    "Todo lo que hemos hecho nos llevado a este momento."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:362
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_32463829:

    # n side sad_side "If we want to truly \"get it out of our systems\" like we were saying, then we need to do this. We need to go all the way." with dissolve
    n side sad_side "Si de verdad queremos \"sacarlo de nuestros sistemas\" como dijimos, tenemos que hacer esto. Debemos ir hasta el final." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:363
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_717750bc:

    # n sad "And I think you would want to further your skill as a hypnotist, right?" with dissolve
    n sad "Y creo que a ti te gustaría mejorar tus habilidades como hipnotista, ¿cierto?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:364
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_cd8a75cc:

    # "She's not even wrong about that."
    "En eso no se equivoca."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:365
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_1465367d:

    # "Besides the fact we've been able to spend so much time together, I've found practicing hypnosis with her to be incredibly fascinating."
    "Además del hecho de que hemos podido pasar tanto tiempo juntos; practicar hipnosis con ella me ha parecido increíblemente fascinante."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:366
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_eb99d80f:

    # ks frown blush "R-Right."
    ks frown blush "C-cierto."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:367
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_faa45032:

    # n sad_side "Right. And just like before, I do want you to have some fun with this, Kyou." with dissolve
    n sad_side "Cierto. E igual que antes, quiero te tú te diviertas un poco con esto, Kyou." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:368
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_7076efea:

    # n "So long as you don't try anything stupid, I'm sure we'll both have a good time while you explore the limits of your abilities."
    n "Siempre y cuando no intentes nada estúpido, estoy segura de que ambos nos la pasaremos muy bien explorando los límites de tus habilidades."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:369
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_4021560f:

    # "Still, even as she says all this, I can't say she looks very comfortable."
    "Sin embargo, por más que esté diciendo todo esto, no puedo decir que se ve muy cómoda."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:370
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_be880052:

    # n sad_closed "B-But, I trust you." with dissolve
    n sad_closed "P-pero, confío en ti." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:371
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_b4488310:

    # "Could it be that she's STILL holding back about what she wants?"
    "¿Será que AÚN está reprimiendo sus deseos?"

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:372
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_71972a14:

    # n front surprised "I never thought I'd be saying it, but... I really do trust you. So much." with dissolve
    n front surprised "Nunca pensé que diría esto, pero... de verdad confío en ti. Mucho." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:426
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_b89ee8e5:

    # n sleepy "The fact all your post-hypnotic suggestions work so well on me... that's proof, isn't it?" with dissolve
    n sleepy "El hecho de que todas tus sugestiones pothipnóticas funcionen tan bien en mí... es prueba de ello, ¿no?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:374
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_68385f61:

    # n frown "So that's why... that's why I want to see it through. I want to explore my fantasies to the fullest." with dissolve
    n frown "Y es por eso... es por eso que quiero hacerlo. Quiero explorar mis fantasías con total plenitud." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:375
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_964f204f:

    # n concerned "With you..." with dissolve
    n concerned "Contigo..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:376
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_bfa19fa3:

    # ks "But what you're asking is..."
    ks "Pero lo que me estás pidiendo es..."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:377
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_2bb479f1:

    # n side sad_closed "Obviously I don't mean for you to try anything permanent. That'd be silly. And obviously impossible." with dissolve
    n side sad_closed "Obviamente no pretendo que instales nada permanente. Eso sería tonto. Y obviamente imposible." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:378
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_e3ab2a24:

    # n "And... and of course you can't literally dominate me through hypnosis. I know that."
    n "Y... y, por supuesto, no puedes dominarme literalmente con hipnosis. Eso lo sé."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:379
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_ee17c3e0:

    # n "But if, just for tonight... if just for a little while, you could convince me that you had total control over my mind?"
    n "Pero ¿y si, solo por esta noche... solo por un rato, pudieras convencerme de que tienes el control absoluto de mi mente?"

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:380
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_0a1b88c3:

    # n front sleeptalk_concerned "Would that be bad? Would that be something you'd want to do?" with dissolve
    n front sleeptalk_concerned "¿Sería malo? ¿Sería algo que quisieras hacer?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:381
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_fb442390:

    # "I'm not gonna lie. The thought of having someone as pretty as her at my beck and call is goddamn arousing, real or not."
    "No mentiré. La idea de tener a alguien tan bonita como ella a mis órdenes es muy excitante, real o no."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:382
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_4f665f7d:

    # "It sure is a fantasy I could get behind..."
    "Es una fantasía que podría perseguir..."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:383
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_ac1be05b:

    # ks "Total control, huh?"
    ks "Control absoluto, ¿eh?"

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:384
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_e02e51a2:

    # n front surprised "I-I-I mean as much as it's possible to seem like that?" with dissolve
    n front surprised "B-b-bueno, ¿tanto como sea posible hacerlo parecer?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:385
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_d7730eb5:

    # ks frown blush "R-... right. Because we know you're always in control, no matter how deeply hypnotized you get."
    ks frown blush "C-... claro. Porque sabemos que siempre tienes el control, sin importar cuán profundamente hipnotizada estés."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:386
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_58c2d67a:

    # n side sad_closed "Right... That's exactly right." with dissolve
    n side sad_closed "Correcto... Exactamente." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:387
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_7ce30a47:

    # "She says that. WE say that. But..."
    "Eso dice. Eso DECIMOS. Pero..."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:388
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_23a79a8a:

    # n "So like I said, I want you to have some fun, but y-... yeah, let's keep it clean, okay?"
    n "Así que, como dije, quiero que te diviertas un poco, pero s-... sí, juguemos limpio, ¿de acuerdo?"

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:389
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_3fdb772f:

    # "Does she really mean what she says? It almost feels like a contradiction."
    "¿Lo que dice es en serio? Casi parece una contradicción."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:390
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_37834792:

    # "Telling me she wants to feel the illusion of being totally controlled, while still insisting there are limits."
    "Decirme que quiere sentir la ilusión de ser completamente controlada, y aun así insistir en que hay límites."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:391
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_b0249c75:

    # "Maybe that's because she's still too shy about what she truly wants?"
    "¿Tal vez sea porque aún es muy tímida para expresar lo que realmente quiere?"

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:393
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_39b69fc2:

    # "What if she's still holding back, even now?"
    "¿Qué tal si aún se está conteniendo?"

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:394
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_063381f2:

    # ks "Okay... i-if you're sure."
    ks "Muy bien... s-si estás tan segura."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:419
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_154c9d82:

    # n front concerned "W-what do you think?" with dissolve
    n front concerned "¿Qu-qué opinas?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:420
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_7b7ea701:

    # ks "It's... T-that is..."
    ks "Es... eso es..."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:422
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_2028f6d7:

    # n angry normal "Oh come {w=0.4}{nw}" with dissolve
    n angry normal "¡Ay, por {w=0.4}FA{nw}" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:476
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_0a4e6da2:

    # n angry normal "Oh come {nw}" with dissolve
    n angry normal "¡Ay, por {nw}" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:423
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_ca95a135:

    # extend "ON, Kyou! How many guys do you think would kill for a chance like this?" with vpunch
    extend "VOR, Kyou! ¿Cuántos chico crees que matarían por una oportunidad así?" with vpunch

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:424
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_ab61efe3:

    # "I jump back a little as she raises her voice, and it jolts my brain back into gear."
    "Oírla elevar la voz me hace dar un pequeño sobre salto, y pone mi cerebro de nuevo en marcha."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:480
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_6d9d789a:

    # "Do I have any serious objections to doing this? Why not try to give her what she wants?" with dissolve
    "¿De verdad tengo alguna objeción a hacer esto? ¿Por qué no intentar darle lo que quiere?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:427
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_66d4fe53:

    # "If she's holding back, then I am too. I should just do it."
    "Si se está conteniendo, yo también. Voy a hacerlo y ya."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:428
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_e0134db1:

    # "And I'll do it in a way she'll approve."
    "Y lo haré de tal forma que ella lo apruebe."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:432
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_1c1cc346:

    # "So with a smirk, I pull my penlight out from its home in my pocket, which immediately grabs Nozomi's attention." with dissolve
    "Así que, sonriente, saco la linterna de su hogar en mi bolsillo, la cual captura inmediatamente la atención de Nozomi." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:433
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_408db2ee:

    # ks smirk "I'll make that the last time you raise your voice to me in this house, young lady."
    ks smirk "Me aseguraré esa sea la última vez que me alzas la voz en esta casa, jovencita."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:438
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_9b30657f:

    # "And with that I flash the light across her eyes, causing her to immediately snap her gaze to it with a peculiar longing."
    "Y dicho eso, paso la luz por sus ojos, haciéndola clavar su mirada en ella de inmediato, con particular anhelo."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:439
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_9dd20283:

    # n "K-kyou..."
    n "K-kyou..."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:441
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_71fe1417:

    # ks smile noblush "Shhh, Nozomi. Don't say anything more."
    ks smile noblush "Shhh, Nozomi. No digas nada más."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:445
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_60626d09:

    # ks smile "We both know you can't resist the light. It's futile of you to try."
    ks smile "Ambos sabemos que no puedes resistirte a la luz. Intentarlo es fútil."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:456
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_be72cad5:

    # "As I finish flashing the light again I reach out and firmly push on her shoulder, causing her to stumble backwards onto the couch behind her."
    "Luego de deslizar el haz una vez más, empujo firmemente su hombro, haciéndola tropezar y caer hacia atrás sobre el sofá."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:459
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_01bc963c:

    # "She already looks out of it as she slumps on the seat."
    "Para cuando se desploma en el asiento ya tiene la mirada perdida."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:460
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_f512ca8c:

    # "I've barely said anything to her, but all her prior conditioning must be doing most of the work for me."
    "Apenas le he dicho nada, pero su acondicionamiento previo debe estar haciendo la mayor parte del trabajo por mí."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:462
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_fdc6b077:

    # "Of course it crossed my mind that I could've just used the spoken trigger to put her under immediately..."
    "Claro que se me ocurrió que podría simplemente usar el ancla verbal para ponerla en trance de inmediato..."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:464
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_c45422fa:

    # "But as I pass the light across her attentive eyes again, I'm certain doing it in this manner is much more fitting for the occasion."
