    "Si algo puede hacer para resistir, probablemente sea evitar que le diga qué hacer en primer lugar."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:626
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_c91a5442:

    # "But I'll just swallow my nerves and just get the words out. I mean, it's not even like she hasn't done this for me before..."
    "Pero voy a tragarme mis nervios y escupir las palabras. Digo, no es como si no hubiera hecho esto conmigo antes."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:627
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_93f833c7:

    # ks frown blush "S-strip down to your underwear, Nozomi."
    ks frown blush "P-ponte en ropa interior, Nozomi."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:628
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_1a6f434e:

    # ncg surprised blush "{size=16}U-uhh?!{/size}" with dissolve
    ncg surprised blush "{size=16}¡¿E-eeh?!{/size}" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:629
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_5eb18233:

    # "Nozomi lets out another whimper as she squirms on the couch."
    "Nozomi suelta otro susurro, retorciéndose en el sofá."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:630
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_6f87a430:

    # "I think I know Nozomi well enough to know her protesting reaction is theater. So I lean in and try to steady my breath as I command her further."
    "Creo que conozco bien a Nozomi como para saber que su reacción de protesta es teatro. Así que me inclino y trato de estabilizar mi respiración para reiterar mi orden."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:631
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_4a518327:

    # ks "That's right, Nozomi. I'm not asking you, and we're not roleplaying characters."
    ks "Así es, Nozomi. No te lo estoy preguntando, y no somos personajes de un juego de rol."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:632
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_4fe6480b:

    # "Raising my hand again, Nozomi quivers on the seat in anticipation."
    "Cuando vuelvo a levantar mi mano, Nozomi se estremece en su asiento con anticipación."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:633
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_bdfc883c:

    # "She can only swivel her widened eyes to watch as I prepare to snap my fingers once again beside her left ear."
    "No puede hacer más que mover sus ojos para observar cómo chasqueo nuevamente los dedos junto a su oreja izquierda."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:636
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_907fab9f:

    # ks "I'm telling you, Nozomi Akemi, to stand up and strip for me." with dissolve
    ks "Ya me oíste, Nozomi Akemi, ponte de pie y desvístete." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:653
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_b4c7eda5:

    # ncg "{size=16}{cps=20}I... I-I ref... {w=0.5}refuse-{/cps}{/size}{w=1.0}{nw}"
    ncg "{size=16}{cps=20}M-... M-me re... {w=0.5}reúso-{/cps}{/size}{w=1.0}{nw}"

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:639
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_f6623175:

    # ks "Stand and strip."
    ks "De pie y desvístete."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:647
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_df321ceb:

    # "I don't know if was specifically the directness of that last command, or if my repeated ordering had simply worn her down..."
    "No sé si fue específicamente por lo directa que fue esa última orden, y si el mandamiento incesante simplemente la agotó..."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:648
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_c5be43ea:

    # "But it's enough to get Nozomi up off the couch and start tugging at her blazer."
    "Pero es suficiente para levantar a Nozomi del sofá y hacerla tirar de su chaqueta."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:649
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_57f53937:

    # "Her body seems to be in a constant state of trembling as she sheds her uniform, keeping her eyes closed the whole time while her cheeks flush deeply."
    "Su cuerpo parece estar en constante temblor al despojarse de su uniforme, cerrando sus ojos en todo momento con sus mejillas al rojo vivo."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:653
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_dd0cfd0b:

    # "And as her skirt joins the rest of her uniform on the floor of my room, I'm made painfully aware of the state of my own body pushing against my pants."
    "Y cuando su falda se une al resto de su uniforme en el suelo de mi sala, de pronto estoy dolorosamente consciente del estado de mi propio cuerpo presionando mis pantalones."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:654
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_86a95458:

    # "But Nozomi told me not to do anything stupid..."
    "Pero Nozomi me dijo que no hiciera nada estúpido..."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:656
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_4fd08463:

    # "I... I can just enjoy her like this, I guess." with dissolve
    "Puedo... puedo disfrutarla así, supongo." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:657
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_daa92176:

    # n "{size=16}O-oh gosh, don't stare at me like that. It's embarrassing...{/size}"
    n "{size=16}A-ay, Dios, no me mires así. Es vergonzoso...{/size}"

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:658
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_9a9b8426:

    # "Ugh. Her saying that is making me blush harder. I gotta remind her who's boss."
    "Ay. Oírla decir eso me hace ruborizarme más. Tengo que recordarle quién manda."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:659
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_af8a134d:

    # ks frown blush "I... g-give the orders around here, Nozomi. So now, I want you to kneel."
    ks frown blush "Yo... s-soy quien da las órdenes aquí, Nozomi. Así que ahora quiero que te arrodilles..."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:663
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_a4fc8278:

    # "Nozomi groans slightly as she finds herself dropping meekly to the floor in front of me."
    "Nozomi gimotea ligeramente, dejándose caer dócilmente al suelo ante mí."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:665
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_f3460893:

    # "Wasn't really expecting that to be so easy, and judging from the embarrassed look she gives me from down there, neither was she." with dissolve
    "No esperaba que fuera tan fácil, y a juzgar por la pena con la que me mira desde abajo, ella tampoco." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:666
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_e19733bf:

    # ks smirk "That's a good girl, Nozomi. Isn't it nicer when you don't resist my commands?"
    ks smirk "Qué buena chica, Nozomi. ¿No es más agradable cuando no resistes mir órdenes?"

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:668
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_eb0996ef:

    # n front pout "{size=16}I am resisting. Kyou... I am, I just...{/size}" with dissolve
    n front pout "{size=16}Estoy resistiendo. Kyou... En serio, es que...{/size}" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:669
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_92d46ffa:

    # "As she cutely protests in near silence, I grin and wag a finger at her."
    "Al escuchar sus lindas y casi mudas protestas, sonrío y le meneo un dedo."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:670
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_bcc062e0:

    # ks "Kyou? That's \"Sir\" to you, Nozomi. Call me \"Sir\" from now on."
    ks "¿Kyou? Es \"Señor\" para ti, Nozomi. Háblame de usted y llámame \"Señor\" de ahora en adelante."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:672
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_bc211193:

    # n "{size=16}Ah... {w=1.0}{nw}{/size}" with dissolve
    n "{size=16}Ah... {w=1.0}{nw}{/size}" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:674
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_888cad82:

    # extend "{size=16}Y-Yes, Sir...{/size}" with dissolve
    extend "{size=16}S-Sí, Señor...{/size}" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:675
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_46decc88:

    # "Man, what a fucking rush. She didn't resist that one either."
    "Cielos, qué puta emoción. Tampoco se resistió a esa order."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:677
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_e8931cb5:

    # "Reaching down to pet her, she looks up at me from the floor and... goddamn, my brain's having all kinds of thoughts right now." with dissolve
    "Acaricio su cabeza, ella me mira desde el suelo y... maldición, mi cerebro está pensando toda clase de cosas." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:678
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_91b1aa08:

    # "A cacophony of ideas ranging from vulgar to chaste, and everything in-between light up inside my mind, while Nozomi looks up at me with a need in her eyes."
    "Una cacofonía de ideas que van desde lo vulgar hasta lo casto, y todo lo que hay de por medio, resuena en mi mente; mientras que Nozomi me observa con necesidad en sus ojos."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:679
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_7a6bbdb1:

    # "But after what feels like an age, one thought wins out."
    "Pero luego de lo que parece una era, una idea gana la contienda."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:681
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_9a687b21:

    # "And having made up my mind, I turn my attention back to my beautifully-entranced captive." with dissolve
    "Y habiéndome decidido, dirijo mi atención a mi cautiva, quien sigue en un hermoso estado de trance." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:682
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_62a68ffa:

    # ks smile "You know, I'm still thinking about the power I have over you. About all the things I could make you do."
    ks smile "¿Sabes?, sigo pensando en el poder que tengo sobre ti. En todas las cosas que podría obligarte a hacer."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:683
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_5fc1989d:

    # ks "And although you may try to resist, we both know you're far too weak-willed to hold out against me."
    ks "Y aunque intentes resistir, ambos sabemos que tu voluntad es demasiado débil para oponerte a mí."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:684
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_2ec66298:

    # ks "Even if you knew my commands would risk your life. Even if my orders would strip you of your very humanity..."
    ks "Incluso si supieras que mis órdenes pondrían en riesgo tu vida. Incluso si supieras que te despojarían de tu humanidad."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:685
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_c0625af5:

    # ks "You'll be powerless to do anything but smile and obey, and accept my total control over your mind."
    ks "No podrías hacer más que sonreír y obedecer, y aceptar el control total que tengo sobre tu mente."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:686
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_69d68624:

    # ks "Doesn't that thought excite you, Nozomi?"
    ks "¿Acaso pensar en eso no te emociona, Nozomi?"

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:689
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_73c3ab85:

    # n "{size=16}It.. it does, Sir. It thrills me to my core to know I'm powerless before you.{/size}"
    n "{size=16}S-... Sí, Señor. Me emociona en lo más profundo saber que soy impotente ante usted.{/size}"

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:690
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_da2cb5d6:

    # ks "So then, Nozomi. With this ultimate power at my disposal I command you to..."
    ks "Entonces, Nozomi. Con el poder absoluto que tengo a mi disposición, te ordeno que..."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:713
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_4d6b1ed7:

    # n "{size=16}...{/size}"
    n "{size=16}...{/size}"

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:715
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_1d0e7881:

    # n "{size=16}H-Huh?!{/size}" with dissolve
    n "{size=16}¿E-Eh?{/size}" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:721
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_fdf2e9d6:

    # "I'm almost as surprised as Nozomi as I watch her rise up from the floor."
    "Estoy casi tan sorprendido como Nozomi, y la observo levantarse del suelo."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:837
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_43b5954d:

    # "All this need I have, and I'm making her do something goofy?" with dissolve
    "¿Siento tanto deseo, y la pongo a hacer una tontería?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:729
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_7ba5a4c7:

    # "But as I watch Nozomi obediently pad towards my kitchen, I think I'm doing the right thing by keeping things light for her."
    "Pero viendo a Nozomi caminar obedientemente a la cocina, creo que estoy haciendo lo correcto al escoger algo pequeño."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:731
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_2bba274c:

    # "... I'm sure I heard a soft chuckle from her as she disappears from view, followed shortly after by the sound of the fridge opening."
    "... Estoy seguro de que oí una risita cuando desapareció de mi vista, seguido poco después por el sonido de mi refrigerador abriéndose."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:732
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_775f5953:

    # "Anyway, something occurred to me while I was giving her my hammy villain speech."
    "En fin, algo se me ocurrió mientras le daba cursi discruso de villano."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:733
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_786a2f15:

    # "I don't know how Nozomi feels in this moment, but it really does seem like I have this absolute power over her."
    "No sé cómo se siente Nozomi en este momento, pero sí se siente como si tuviera poder absoluto sobre ella."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:734
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_1d3bdb99:

    # "And if that's true, I... I do need to be careful with it."
    "Y si eso es verdad, yo... necesito tener cuidado con eso."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:735
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_3afa4be4:

    # "Hurting Nozomi is the absolute last thing I want to do."
    "Hacerle daño es absolutamente lo último que quiero."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:736
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_f259575c:

    # "But while I'm thinking that, I also realize I'm missing the sight of an underwear-clad girl cooking for me..."
    "Pero mientras pienso en eso, también me doy cuenta de que me estoy perdiendo de una chica en ropa interior cocinando para mí."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:737
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_e44dd0c4:

    # "I gotta follow her!"
    "¡Tengo que seguirla!"

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:739
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_234917b1:

    # "Taking a seat at the dining table, I simply watch with a grin as Nozomi works, navigating around my kitchen with relative ease to get her task done."
    "Con una sonrisa, tomo asiento en el comedor y la observo trabajar, navegando por mi cocina con relativa facilidad para terminar su tarea."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:741
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_a5e47e8d:

    # "I can tell she's a little flustered at my staring, but she doesn't say anything as she prepares the food, sets it on a plate and serves it up to me at the table." with dissolve
    "Puedo notar que la pone un poco nerviosa que la mire, pero prepara la comida sin decir nada, la coloca en un plato y la sirve en la mesa para mí." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:742
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_655e6fd5:

    # n side sad "{size=16}H-Here you are, Sir.{/size}" with dissolve
    n side sad "{size=16}B-buen provecho, Señor.{/size}" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:743
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_6cde1bce:

    # "I take a look at the cheese omelette in front of me, then at her, still grinning."
    "Le echo un vistazo al omelet de queso que tengo delante, luego a ella, sin dejar de sonreír."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:744
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_3de11c0a:

    # ks smirk "I never said I wanted to eat it, Nozo. Besides, I'm not hungry."
    ks smirk "Nunca dije que quería comerlo, Nozo. Además, no tengo hambre."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:745
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_0254c62b:

    # n frown "{size=16}What? Then why did you have me make it? Geez.{/size}" with dissolve
    n frown "{size=16}¿Qué? ¿Entonces por qué me hico prepararlo? Caray.{/size}" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:746
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_8e452eea:

    # ks "Sit down and eat it yourself."
    ks "Siéntate y cómetelo tú."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:879
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_432114b1:

    # n "{size=16}Ahhn...{/size}"
    n "{size=16}Aaah...{/size}"

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:750
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_ceee94e2:

    # "Damn, she's just getting turned on by any order I give her now."
    "Diablos, cada orden que le doy solo la prende más."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:753
