    # n front pout "{size=16}But I'm not hungry either...{/size}" with dissolve
    n front pout "{size=16}Pero tampoco tengo hambre...{/size}" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:754
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_f7ec5f10:

    # "She says, as she tears a piece off and pops it into her mouth."
    "Dice ella, cortando un trozo e introduciéndolo a su boca."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:755
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_5e87599b:

    # n "{size=16}Mmth... Jerk.{/size}"
    n "{size=16}Mmn... Cretino.{/size}"

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:756
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_14fa03e8:

    # ks smile "Tell me how you're really feeling, Nozomi."
    ks smile "Dime cómo te sientes en realidad, Nozomi."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:758
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_97cd4546:

    # "She takes a moment to swallow her food..." with dissolve
    "Hace una pausa para tragar su comida..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:760
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_2a35edd5:

    # "Then pushes another piece of omelette past her lips, seemingly to avoid answering me." with dissolve
    "Luego empuja otro pedazo de omelet por sus labios, probablemente para evitar contestarme." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:761
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_b7ee1939:

    # "It gets a laugh out of me as she pouts, knowing what's coming as I bring my hand beside her head."
    "Y me río al verla hacer un puchero, sabiendo con qué intensiones levanto mi mano junto a su cabeza."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:762
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_7df275d2:

    # "I have ways of making you talk, Nozo."
    "Tengo métodos para hacerte hablar, Nozo."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:765
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_ee5f32dd:

    # ks "Tell me how you're feeling right now, Nozomi." with dissolve
    ks "Dime cómo te sientes en este momento, Nozomi." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:766
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_1b4358e6:

    # n pout_left "{size=16}Ahn... I... I-I feel good, Sir.{/size}" with dissolve
    n pout_left "{size=16}Aah... M... M-me siento bien, Señor.{/size}" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:767
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_42b8c06e:

    # n sigh "{size=16}I know it's just a simple thing, but even making me do this and knowing I can't stop myself is so euphoric you wouldn't believe.{/size}" with dissolve
    n sigh "{size=16}Sé que es algo muy simple, pero incluso ser obligada a hacer esto y saber que no me puedo detener me causa más euforia de la que se imagina.{/size}" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:904
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_b06c2f9d:

    # "She stops to take another bite of the omelette; her compulsion to obey my latest order conflicting with the previous." with dissolve
    "Se detiene para darle otro mordisco al omelet; su impulso por obedecer mi más reciente orden entra en conflicto con la anterior." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:769
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_eb7d1323:

    # ks neutral "Yet you still look a bit tense to me."
    ks neutral "Aunque yo aún te veo un poco tensa."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:771
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_6c5b29a2:

    # n side sad "{size=16}It's still embarrassing to admit all of this to you. And to myself.{/size}" with dissolve
    n side sad "{size=16}Sigue siendo vergonzoso admitirle todo esto a usted. Y a mí misma.{/size}" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:786
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_8a7dd692:

    # ks smile blush "Nozomi, there's no reason to feel embarrassed about feeling this way. You like what you like."
    ks smile blush "Nozomi, sentirte así no es nada de qué avergonzarse. Lo que te gusta te gusta."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:788
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_f485605e:

    # ks "Also, no one else needs to know if you don't want to say anything. We had a deal." with dissolve
    ks "Además, nadie más debe saber si no quieres decir nada. Tenemos un trato, ¿recuerdas?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:789
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_023d553f:

    # ks "So don't feel ashamed about who you are. You're safe here, with someone who wants you to be happy."
    ks "Así que no sientas pena de ser quién eres. Estás a salvo aquí, con alguien que quiere que seas feliz."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:928
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_e25e95be:

    # ks "Let yourself enjoy this." with dissolve
    ks "Disfrútalo." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:792
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_fe59ddc5:

    # "Nozomi gives me a smile from across the table and nods, still half-chewing as she responds in her cute whispered voice." with dissolve
    "Nozomi me lanza una sonrisa desde el otro lado de la mesa y asiente, y sin dejar del todo de masticar, responde:" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:793
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_61c40fb0:

    # n "{size=16}Thank you, Sir. That does actually make me feel better.{/size}"
    n "{size=16}Gracias, Señor. Eso me hace sentir mejor.{/size}"

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:794
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_3d9f7bfa:

    # "I smile back at her as we enjoy a moment of shared bliss."
    "Le devuelvo la sonrisa y ambos compartimos este momento de dicha."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:795
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_28d9f3e0:

    # "And then with a grin, I'm the one to break the silence for a change."
    "Luego, con malicia, soy yo quien rompe el silencio, para variar."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:796
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_19b452d3:

    # ks smirk "Now be a good girl and finish your omelette, and wash everything up when you're done."
    ks smirk "Ahora sé una buena chica y termina tu omelet, y limpia todo cuando acabes."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:798
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_fecb6bff:

    # "She pokes her tongue out at me, then takes another bite of her food." with dissolve
    "Me saca la lengua, para luego tomar otro bocado de su comida." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:801
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_ea0d63a2:

    # "Soon after she was done in the kitchen I had her get dressed and ready to leave."
    "Poco después, cuando su trabajo en la cocina hubo acabado, hice que se vistiera, lista para partir."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:802
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_ee525a79:

    # "Not that I wanted to, but dad's going to be home soon, and I don't think either of us want to explain this to him of all people."
    "No es que quiera, pero papá volverá a casa pronto, y no creo que ninguno de los dos quiera explicarle esto a nadie, mucho menos a él."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:803
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_dc146684:

    # ks smile "You got everything?"
    ks smile "¿Tienes todo?"

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:804
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_4c10b5d4:

    # n "{size=16}Yes, Sir. Are we doing this again tomorrow?{/size}"
    n "{size=16}Sí, Señor. ¿Volveremos a hacerlo mañana?{/size}"

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:805
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_6ce3cc38:

    # "I respond with a wink and a knowing smirk."
    "Respondo con un guiño y una sonrisa."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:806
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_5c91c90b:

    # ks smirk "Oh, you WILL be coming back here tomorrow. Do I make myself clear?"
    ks smirk "Oh, tú VAS a regresar aquí mañana. ¿Quedó claro?"

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:808
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_6fcf8645:

    # "She replies with a muted giggle." with dissolve
    "Ella contesta con una risita muda." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:809
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_91bf6307:

    # n "{size=16}Yes, Sir. I must obey~{/size}"
    n "{size=16}Sí, Señor. Debo obedecer.{/size}"

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:815
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_2b051346:

    # "For Kyou, it's obvious that they should be a true couple."
    "Para Kyou es obvio que deben ser pareja."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:816
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_f2d1e978:

    # "Nozomi's said herself more than once that she trusts Kyou, and they've done all this kinky stuff together. \"More than friends\" stuff..."
    "Nozomi dijo ella misa más de una vez que confía en Kyou, ya han hecho todas estas cositas picantes juntos. Cosas de \"Más que amigos\"."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:817
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_a8dbfefd:

    # "Kyou knows she's still embarrassed about her kink and her growing relationship with Kyou, but he \"knows\" this is where they're headed."
    "Kyou sabe que sigue avergonzada de sus gustos y de su creciente relación con Kyou, pero él \"sabe\" que todo los ha llevado a esto."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:818
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_7fcc72e1:

    # "And Nozomi can't move on until she accepts her feelings for Kyou and the relationship they're in."
    "Y Nozomi no puede avanzar hasta que acepte sus sentimientos por Kyou y su relación. "

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:819
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_5c135364:

    # "Nozomi's initial resistance to his command doesn't surprise Kyou; knowing how stubborn she is about this." with dissolve
    "La resistencia inicial de Nozomi a su orden no sorprende a Kyou, sabiendo lo obstinada que es al respecto." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:821
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_f3f75fe0:

    # "So he commands her again with a snap of his fingers. Again she refuses."
    "Por lo que repite la orden chasqueando sus dedos. Una vez más, se reúsa."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:828
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_c55dafc1:

    # "A third time, and rather than finally admit it, Nozomi tries to get up and away from Kyou and his snapping fingers."
    "La tercera vez, en lugar de finalmente admitirlo, Nozomi intenta levantarse y alejarse se Kyou y sus chasquidos."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:832
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_b7830fff:

    # "When Kyou again tries to compel her, she grabs his hand and tries telling him to stop!" with vpunch
    "¡Cuando Kyou hace otro intento por obligarla, ella toma su mano e intenta decirle que se detenga!" with vpunch

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:833
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_c31e28df:

    # "Although she can't shout, there's a menace about her whispered demand that temporarily causes Kyou to doubt himself."
    "Si bien no puede gritar, sus susurros son amenazantes, lo cual hace a Kyou dudar por un momento."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:834
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_bea29b11:

    # "She does seem genuine, but couldn't she be playing to her fantasies still?"
    "Parece ser sincera, ¿pero será que sigue metida en sus fantasías?"

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:835
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_b9d4ae44:

    # "Maybe if he tried once more..."
    "Tal vez si lo vuelve a intentar..."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:838
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_b1ceba13:

    # "Nozomi is still clutching his hand tightly, trying to stop him from clicking his fingers."
    "Nozomi aprieta con mucha fuerza la mano de Kyou, intentando evitar que truene los dedos."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:839
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_925fe666:

    # "And Kyou isn't so good at clicking with his other hand, but it doesn't matter."
    "Y Kyou no es bueno chasqueando con la zurda, pero eso no importa."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:842
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_a5111ee9:

    # "Instead, Kyou waves his free hand across Nozomi's face, and despite her protests she immediately falls silent with a blank expression as he speaks." with dissolve
    "En vez de eso, Kyou mueve su mano libre frente al rostro de Nozomi y, a pesar de sus protestas, se queda en silencio al instante y su expresión se pone en blanco mientras él habla." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:844
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_fd5b6932:

    # "Instead, Kyou uses his free hand to poke Nozomi's forehead, and despite her protests she immediately falls silent with a blank expression as he speaks." with dissolve
    "En vez de eso, Kyou usa su mano libre para tocar la frente de Nozomi y, a pesar de sus protestas, se queda en silencio al instante y su expresión se pone en blanco mientras él habla." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:845
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_e65da867:

    # "This time, when he tells her to agree to be his girlfriend, the suggestion takes immediately."
    "Esta vez, cuando le dice que acepte ser su novia, la sugestión entra de inmediato."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:847
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_04a0be8b:

    # "Nozomi smiles as she comes out of her blank state." with dissolve
    "Nozomi sale de su estado de trance con una sonrisa." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:848
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_189b4a57:

    # "So there, her resistance was clearly all for show, and now Kyou's lifted her of her anxiety about starting a proper relationship with him. All is good."
    "Ahí lo tienes, su resistencia no era más que teatro, y Kyou la ha liberado de su ansiedad por formar una verdadera relación con él."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:849
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_a1817f1b:

    # "They'll probably declare their love for each other, and keen to keep their kinky hypno session going, Kyou shyly orders Nozomi to follow him to his bedroom..."
    "Probablemente declaren su amor el uno por el otro, y deseoso de continuar con sus pícaras sesiones de hipnosis, Kyou le ordena tímidamente a Nozomi a seguirlo a su habitación..."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:851
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_ad008b7a:

    # "... And of course now we fade to black here and timeskip to an epilogue, for uh... obvious reasons given the general tone of the game."
    "... Y, por supuesto, la pantalla se pone en negro y hay un salto de tiempo hasta el epílogo, por, eh... obvias razones relacionadas al tono del juego."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:852
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_acabd613:

    # "The epilogue itself would have shades of the Delusion ending, where Kyou also has Nozomi hypnotized into being his girlfriend."
    "El epílogo en sí tendrá matices del final de la ruta Deliro, en la cual Kyou también hipnotiza a Nozomi para que sea su novia."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:853
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_145b790d:

    # "Only in this version, Kyou probably doesn't have the shock realization that he does there."
    "Solo que, en esta versión, Kyou probablemente no tendrá la repentina
Iluminación que tuvo ahí."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:854
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_5a93f410:

    # "After all, he's sure Nozomi wanted it this way, where he's controlling her via hypnosis and she's living out her fantasy with him."
    "Después de todo, está seguro de que Nozomi quería esto, que la contralara con hipnosis y ahora está viviendo su fantasía con él."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:855
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_05162173:

    # "But like in Delusion, he's finding out how unsatisfying it is to have a girlfriend who can't think for herself."
    "Pero, al igual que en Delirio, está descubriendo lo poco satisfactorio que es tener una novia que no puede pensar por sí misma."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:856
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_dde88054:

    # "Only he's still going along with it because this is what he wanted too, wasn't it? Even if the spark is gone..."
    "Pero le sigue el juego, porque esto es lo que ella quería, ¿no? Por más que se haya ido la chispa... "

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:858
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_8e58a8a5:

    # "Kyou can't get out of his head the fact that Nozomi said straight up last week, before they got too involved, that she was not interested in dating."
    "Kyou no puede sacarse de la cabeza el hecho de que Nozomi dijo explícitamente la semana pasada, entes de involucrarse, que no estaba interesada en salir con nadie."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:859
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_e3f7cfcf:

    # "While the two of them have flirted with this total control hypno power play, Kyou realizes there are some lines he shouldn't cross..."
    "Si bien los dos se la han pasado coqueteando con este juego de control hipnótico absoluto, Kyou se da cuenta de que hay línea que no debe curzar..."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:861
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_8a529309:

    # "And much as he hates to admit, this is probably one of them for Nozomi. So he relents and apologizes to her." with dissolve
    "Y por mucho que odie admitirlo, esta probablemente es una de ellas para Nozomi. Por lo que desiste y se disculpa con ella." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:862
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_e7a6366a:

    # "Nozomi breathes a sigh of relief and appreciates him stopping, and would also like to stop the play they've been doing."
    "Nozomi suelta un suspiro de alivio y aprecia que haya parado, y además le gustaría terminar el juego."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:864
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_69f33e79:

    # "Skip forward a few minutes, where Nozomi's dressed again, having been deprogrammed of the night's suggestions."
    "Nos adelantamos unos cuantos minutos, a cuando Nozomi está de nuevo vestida y desprogramada de las sugestiones de esta noche."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:865
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_a69b28ee:

    # "They're now starting to talk about what happened."
    "Ahora empiezan a hablar de lo que pasó."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:866
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_2d6aeaa1:

    # "The experience has left her spooked, and she can't explain how she came so close to accepting something that she knew wasn't true."
    "La experiencia la dejó espantada, y no puede explicar lo cerca que estuvo de aceptar algo que sabía que no era cierto."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:867
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_3300c445:

    # "That revelation stings for Kyou, but what does it mean? Was their hidden observer theory false? Was Nozomi going along with things she wasn't comfortable with?"
    "La revelación es dolorosa para Kyou, ¿pero qué significa? ¿Su teoría del efecto del observador oculto era falsa? ¿Nozomi estaba siguiendo cosas con las que no estaba cómoda?"

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:869
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_372760c1:

    # "I can't resist. I have to know how far Nozomi's willing to go to realize her fantasy to be powerless."
    "No me puedo resistir. Tengo que saber qué tan lejos está dispuesta a ir Nozomi por vivir su fantasía de ser impotente."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:871
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_fc62d7aa:

    # "I've seen just how excellent she is at being hypnotized and following instructions. But surely everyone has a limit."
    "Ya he visto lo excelente que es siendo hipnotizada y siguiendo instrucciones. Pero todos tienen un límite."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:872
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_03b8ed47:

    # "And in the context of this hypnotic power play of ours, there seems no better time for us to find out."
    "Y en el contexto de este juego de poder hipnótico, este parece el mejor momento para averiguarlo."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:873
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_67fc1991:

    # ks "Become blank for me, Nozomi."
    ks "Apaga tu mente, Nozomi."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:875
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_1d0e7881_1:

    # n "{size=16}H-Huh?!{/size}" with dissolve
    n "{size=16}¡¿E-eh?!{/size}" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:876
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_12d57b26:

    # "Nozomi squeaks her dissent quietly, but I think she's just confused about what I want her to do."
    "Nozomi expone silenciosamente su disidencia, pero creo que solo esta confundida con lo que le estoy pidiendo."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:877
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_e2e5fed2:

    # "After all, this is another thing she's pretty much done for me before."
    "Después de todo, esto también ya lo ha hecho antes por mí."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:878
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_0ae23b65:

    # ks smirk "Nozomi, you will empty your mind of every thought in that pretty little head of yours."
    ks smirk "Nozomi, vaciarás de todo pensamiento esa linda cabecita tuya."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:879
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_6ec17945:

    # n "{size=16}I... i-i...{/size}"
    n "{size=16}Y... y-yo...{/size}"

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:881
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_9942ec3d:

    # "Ignoring her meek protest, I bring my hand in front of her face once more and snap my fingers again." with dissolve
    "Ignorando sus dóciles protestas, pongo mi mano frente a su rostro una vez más y trueno los dedos." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:883
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_e1438fef:

    # ks "Stay kneeling for me and clear all the thoughts from your head."
    ks "Quédate de rodillas y despoja tu cabeza de todo pensamiento."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:885
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_7a1f8507:

    # n "{size=16}A... a-all the thoughts.{/size}" with dissolve
    n "{size=16}T... t-todo pensamiento.{/size}" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:887
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_98ffa85d:

    # ks "Completely mindless now, Nozomi... No thoughts at all."
    ks "Mente completamente apagada, Nozomi. Ni un solo pensamiento."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:890
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_26c6d0c4:

    # "I watch as her head slumps forward, and I can see her expression go completely slack while a sliver of drool escapes her lips to drop on the floor by her hands."
    "Veo su cabeza caer hacia adelante, y puedo notar cómo su expresión se queda en blanco, mientras una gota de saliva escapa de sus labios y cae junto a sus manos. "

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:891
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_739e6519:

    # ks "Good girl, Nozomi. Completely obedient. Completely mindless. Powerless to do anything but accept my total control over your mind."
    ks "Buena chica, Nozomi. Completamente obediente. Mente apagada. Sin poder para hacer nada más que aceptar el control absoluto que tengo sobre tu mente."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:892
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_1889cf03:

    # "After I'm done filling her imagination, I sit there quietly and continue to watch her still form."
    "Cuando termino de llenar su imaginación, sentado en silencio, observo lo inmóvil que está."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:893
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_38144cbd:

    # "The more I watch her, the more I can believe she truly is as helpless as she looks."
    "Entre más la miro, más fácil es creer que de verdad es tan impotente como aparenta."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:894
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_fe9950bf:

    # "And the more I wonder if I can take that helplessness even further."
    "Y más me pregunto si puedo llevar esa impotencia todavía más allá."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:895
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_45a0f6a6:

    # ks "So mindless, Nozomi, that you won't even think to respond to outside stimulation."
    ks "Tu mente está tan apagada, Nozomi, que ni siquiera pensarás en responder a estímulos externos."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:897
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_a99d196d:

    # "Crouching down beside her now, still watching over her unmoving, slackened face, I have to see how fully she can take to such a command." with dissolve
    "Me agacho junto a ella, viendo su flojo e inmovilizado rostro, tengo que ver qué tan a fondo puede tomar una orden así." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:898
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_64213c48:

    # "Could she possibly be able to ignore the very real stimulation of her body to such an extent?"
    "¿De verdad será capaz de ignorar cualquier estímulo en su cuerpo hasta tal punto?"

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:899
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_e7ba5721:

    # "I begin by tentatively poking her cheek. First gently, then much more firmly."
    "Comienzo tocando con cuidado so mejilla. Primero con gentileza, luego mucho más fuerte."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:900
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_aa106baf:

    # "Besides pushing her skin aside, it accomplishes nothing."
    "Además de empujar su piel, eso no logra nada."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:901
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_4d9f6b1d:

    # "Maybe if I blew in her ear?"
    "¿Tal vez si le soplo en la oreja?"

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:902
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_c81c90e2:

    # "Nope, the only reaction I get is from myself as I chuckle at the experience."
    "Nop. La única reacción que obtengo es mía en forma de risa."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:904
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_e7afb216:

    # "But surely she'll be forced to react if I were to suddenly reach over to her foot and start teasing the sole with my fingertips."
    "Pero definitivamente tendrá que reaccionar y me acerco a su pie de repente y tiento su suela con las yemas de mis dedos."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:905
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_bb2cf764:

    # n "..."
    n "..."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:906
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_151eb7b3:

    # "Wow. Okay. I know tickling the sole of her foot like this should have her squealing."
    "Guau. Muy bien. Sé que hacerle cosquillas en los pies así debería hacerla chillar."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:907
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_ed766e51:

    # "But I soon stop my efforts when it seems I may as well be trying to tickle the sofa."
    "Pero pronto detengo mis esfuerzos, pues, por lo que parece, bien podría estar haciéndole cosquillas al sofá."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:910
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_8163f55e:

    # "But surely she'll be forced to react if I were to suddenly reach over and slap my hand down harshly on her butt." with vpunch
    "Pero definitivamente tendrá que reaccionar si me acerco de repente y le doy una fuerte nalgada." with vpunch

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:911
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_bb2cf764_1:

    # n "..."
    n "..."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:912
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_f0b51f8b:

    # "Wow. Okay. But if I went in harder..."
    "Guau. Muy bien. ¿Qué tal más fuerte...?"

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:914
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_76f75624:

    # n "..." with vpunch
    n "..." with vpunch

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:915
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_12696bbc:

    # "All I manage to do is make my hand sting. She didn't even flinch, let alone make any kind of noise."
    "Lo único que logro es que me pique la mano. Ni siquiera se inmutó, mucho menos hizo ningún ruido."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:916
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_9e7fe582:

    # "That's seriously impressive, Nozomi."
    "Eso en serio es impresionante, Nozomi."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:917
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_47428fd0:

    # "So she refuses to react in any way, just as I commanded her."
    "Se reúsa a reaccionar de ninguna manera, tal como le ordené."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:918
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_fe1291c3:

    # "How would she respond if I commanded her again?"
    "¿Cómo respondería si le doy otra orden?"

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:919
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_d8e41495:

    # ks neutral "Stand up, Nozomi."
    ks neutral "Levántate, Nozomi."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:925
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_684f6f1b:

    # "I'm not left wondering, as Nozomi climbs back to her feet the moment my command leaves my lips."
    "No me quedo con la duda, pues Nozomi vuelve a ponerse de pie en el instante en que mi orden escapa de mis labios."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:928
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_0ce87976:

    # "What else would she do if I told her?"
    "¿Qué más hará si se lo digo?"

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:929
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_c69d0db4:

    # ks frown blush "Take... t-t-... take off your underwear, Nozomi."
    ks frown blush "Qui-... qu-qu... quítate la ropa interior, Nozomi."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:931
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_9333ea42:

    # "There's not a whisper of complaint, nor any kind of tension in her body as she reaches immediately to pull her undergarments away..."
    "Sin la más mínima queja, sin ninguna clase de tensión en su cuerpo, comienza a tirar de inmediato de su ropa interior..."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:934
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_8e1c90f8:

    # "Nothing but quiet, mindless obedience." with dissolve
    "Nada más que muda y siega obediencia." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:936
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_4a2caf4d:

    # "It sure does seem that commanding Nozomi to rid herself of all thoughts also wiped out any notion of resistance."
    "Al parecer ordenarle a Nozomi que se despojara de todo pensamiento también destruyó cualquier noción de resistencia."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:937
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_9dc8218f:

    # "And this time there's none of her former embarrassment as my eyes can't help but take in every inch of her."
    "Y esa vergüenza de hace rato ahora está completamente ausente, aunque mis ojos no puedan evitar absorber cada centímetro de su ser."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:938
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_254b1f10:

    # "She's... She's as beautiful as I imagined her to be."
    "Es... Es tan hermosa como la imaginé."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:939
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_f2e9f8b3:

    # "I don't know how long I'm standing there before I'm able to clear my throat and get some more words out of me."
    "No sé cuánto tiempo estuve aquí parado antes de lograr aclararme la garganta y formar más palabras."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1207
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_bd97fbb5:

    # ks blush "S-so... what are you feeling right now, Nozomi? Anything?"
    ks blush "Y-y... ¿qué es lo que sientes ahora, Nozomi? ¿Algo?"

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:941
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_bb2cf764_2:

    # n "..."
    n "..."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:942
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_41d81e6f:

    # ks "Nothing, huh?"
    ks "Nada, ¿eh?"

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:943
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_a21b79bd:

    # ks "I... I-I guess that makes sense for someone with no thoughts, huh."
    ks "S-... S-supongo que tiene sentido para alguien sin pensamientos."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:944
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_bb2cf764_3:

    # n "..."
    n "..."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:945
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_15a10f10:

    # "Okay... So here's the question burning in my mind now, distracted only by what's welling up in my pants from looking over a perfectly naked Nozomi:"
    "Muy bien... Pues hay una pregunta que ahora está ardiendo en mi mente, solo distraída por lo que está brotando en mis pantalones al mirar a una perfectamente desnuda Nozomi:"

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:946
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_cc4b5cc3:

    # "Has she attained true mindlessness? Or is something still in there, waiting to intervene if her comfort or safety are seriously threatened?"
    "¿Su mente se ha apagado por completo? ¿O aún hay algo ahí esperando intervenir si su comodidad y seguridad se ven seriamente amenazadas?"

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:947
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_4e421643:

    # "That whole \"Hidden observer effect\" that we were talking about. Because what a time to truly test that theory."
    "Ese \"Efecto del observador oculto\" del que habíamos hablado. Este es el momento perfecto para poner a prueba esa teoría."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:948
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_f782f2c4:

    # "Maybe Nozomi's content to let me take things as far as this. She did say she trusted me, after all."
    "Tal vez Nozomi esté contenta dejándome llevar las cosas tan lejos. Dijo que confiaba en mí, después de todo."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:949
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_102313bb:

    # "But what if I introduced just a little danger? What then?"
    "Pero ¿qué tal si introdujera solo un poco de peligro? ¿Qué pasaría?"

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:950
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_f39aa8cd:

    # "If I ordered her to do something that would threaten her life if followed through... Would she?"
    "Si le ordenara hacer algo que pusiera en riesgo su vida... ¿lo haría?"

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:953
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_d6b022b8:

    # ks "Nozomi... Stop breathing. I order you to stop breathing."
    ks "Nozomi... Deja de respirar. Te ordeno que dejes de respirar."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:955
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_c773030b:

    # "Fascinating... I'm sure she'll obey, at least initially."
    "Fascinante... Estoy seguro de que obedecerá, al menos al principio."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:956
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_b4647042:

    # "And as I hold a finger under her nose to check her breathing, I wonder..."
    "Y poniendo un dedo bajo su nariz para revisar su respiración, me pregunto..."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:957
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_27592f9d:

    # "How long will she last before she finally allows herself to snap out of this fantasy and let reality take over?"
    "¿Cuánto tiempo seguirá así antes de finalmente despertar de esta fantasía y dejar que la realidad tome el control?"

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:958
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_4f73ccf4:

    # "Or will it be her self-preservation instinct that has to do it for her? Is her mind truly that disciplined?"
    "¿O será su instinto de autopreservación el que lo haga por ella? ¿Su mente de verdad está así de disciplinada?"

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:964
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_050cd9ec:

    # ks "Aren't you going to breathe, Nozomi?"
    ks "¿No vas a respirar, Nozomi?"

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:965
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_10e5768b:

    # "Immediately her barely-audible reply slips past her idle lips."
    "Inmediatamente, una respuesta apenas audible brota de sus labios."

