# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1508
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_e44cd16b:

    # s "\"My dad picked me up from the nurse's office. Just one more humiliation I have had to endure lately.\""
    s "\"Mi papá me recogió de la enfermería. Una humillación más que tuve que soportar recientemente.\""

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1509
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_43413457:

    # "Hearing that makes me remember what she said last week, about not wanting her parents to find out she missed first period that day..."
    "Escuchar eso me hace recordar lo que dijo la semana pasada, sobre no querer que sus padres se enteraran de que se perdió el primer periodo ese día..."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1510
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_77eee88c:

    # ks noblush "This is Hiroko's fault."
    ks noblush "Esto es culpa de Hiroko."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1511
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_c362f656:

    # s "\"Hm?\""
    s "\"¿Mm?\""

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1512
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_0e2e65ab:

    # ks "I can't believe she'd talk to you like that."
    ks "No puedo creer que te hablara así."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1513
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_5a1bf849:

    # s "\"Do not be upset with her. I understand why she said what she said.\""
    s "\"No estés molesto con ella. Entiendo por qué dijo lo que dijo.\""

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:3632
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_3e3d10fb:

    # s "\"... Perhaps this is what needed to happen.\""
    s "\"... Tal vez era necesario que esto ocurriera.\""

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1515
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_683323db:

    # ks surprised "Huh? What do you mean by that?"
    ks surprised "¿Eh? ¿Qué quieres decir?"

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1516
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_06398373:

    # "She sighs."
    "Suspira."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1517
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_9693c420:

    # s "\"Do not worry about it. My dad was surprisingly understanding of my situation, anyway.\""
    s "\"No te preocupes por ello. De cualquier forma, mi papá fue sorprendentemente comprensivo con mi situación.\""

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1518
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_9c9209db:

    # s "\"Although he has demanded I take the rest of the week off.\""
    s "\"Aunque demandó que me tomara el resto de la semana.\""

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1519
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_ba79cffd:

    # s "\"No study, no school of any kind. Just rest and recreation.\""
    s "\"Nada de estudio ni escuela de ningún tipo. Solo descanso y recreación.\""

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1520
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_c38bb758:

    # s "\"Quite the punishment for skipping out of school early, don't you think?\""
    s "\"Vaya castigo por escaparme de la escuela, ¿no te parece?\""

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1521
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_7722a61f:

    # "She jokes, but I don't think she put a lot of effort in that delivery. Like she doesn't really believe it."
    "Está bromeando, pero no creo que le haya puesto mucho esfuerzo. Como si no lo creyera realmente."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1522
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_31a526fb:

    # "Or she's just that tired."
    "O es que así de cansada está."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:3713
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_12a3c845:

    # s "\"Anyway, I wanted to let you know I'll be fine... No, I *am* fine.\""
    s "\"En fin, quería hacerte saber que estaré bien... No, *estoy* bien.\""

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1524
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_4ddc3f23:

    # ks smile blush "Yeah, that's... That's great, Sayori."
    ks smile blush "Sí, eso... Eso es grandioso, Sayori."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1525
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_7cbbd510:

    # "Dammit. There's more I want to say to her."
    "Demonios. Quiero decirle más."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1526
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_2f23ecec:

    # "But I guess I should let her go."
    "Pero supongo que debo dejarla ir."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1527
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_e077a011:

    # ks "I'll see you next week."
    ks "Te veo la próxima semana."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1528
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_347416dd:

    # s "\"Not so fast, Mr. Koyama. I am not quite done with you.\""
    s "\"No tan rápido, Sr. Koyama. Aún no he terminado contigo.\""

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1529
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_c67eb3c9:

    # "I can feel the hairs spring from my neck when she says that."
    "Puedo sentir los pelos ponerse de punta en mi cuello al oírla decir eso."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1530
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_bd9c6c46:

    # "Maybe she's not having the best day of her life, but it sure feels like she's getting some of her edge back at least."
    "Tal vez no esté teniendo el mejor día de su vida, pero al menos parece que se está recuperando un poco."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1531
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_8b95982e:

    # s "\"I will be lying low, but I do want to see you again before the week is out.\""
    s "\"Estaré agazapada, pero quiero volver a verte antes de que la semana termine.\""

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1532
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Sayori_Doll_46c0accb:

    # s "\"After all, you and I have some unfinished business...\""
    s "\"Después de todo, tú y yo tenemos algunos asuntos pendientes…\""

# TODO: Translation updated at 2020-11-30 19:20

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1543
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_83c89e6c:

    # "Kyou walks into school a few days later with a lump in his throat."
    "Kyou camina a la escuela unos días después con un nudo en la garganta."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1544
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_938be245:

    # "He has a plan. A stupid, desperate, even suicidal plan..."
    "Tiene un plan. Un plan estúpido, desesperado e incluso suicida..."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1545
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_1d8b1f9d:

    # "But if he truly wants to make amends, it's the best he can do..."
    "Pero si en serio quiere enmendar las cosas, es lo mejor que puede hacer..."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1547
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_0ca79871:

    # "So he shows up for class, noting how the hostility towards him remains at a level of simmering contempt."
    "Así que llega a clase, notando que la hostilidad hacia él aún hierve con la misma fuerza."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1548
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_c0b8c74c:

    # "He notes that Akiko fails to acknowledge him. Whether because she's intimidated by the rest of the class or disgusted in unison with them, he can't say."
    "Nota que Akiko aún no reconoce su presencia. Ya sea porque se siente intimidada por el resto de la clase, o porque siente tanto asco como ellos. Ni idea."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1549
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_7b4ac267:

    # "He just has to go through the motions until school is out..."
    "Simplemente tendrá que seguir adelante hasta que las clases terminen..."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1552
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_11f093bb:

    # "Just cleaning time to go..."
    "Ya solo queda la hora de la limpieza..."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1556
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_b3e6904d:

    # "He's with Akiko and several other students cleaning the corridor today."
    "Hoy le toca limpiar el corredor con Akiko y algunos estudiantes más."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1557
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_69055b2c:

    # "As they start, Kyou remarks that his cleaning cloth is ragged and he needs to get a new one."
    "Cuando empiezan, Kyou menciona que su trapo está rasgado y debe ir por uno nuevo."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1559
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_367ddb20:

    # "Akiko's like sure, whatever. Hurry back." with dissolve
    "Akiko responde: sí, claro, como sea. Date prisa." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1561
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_688848b8:

    # "It stings, hearing Akiko so dismissive towards him. But he tries to put it out of his mind as he goes to fetch a fresh cloth."
    "Duele oír a Akiko dirigirse a él con tanto desprecio. Pero intenta no pensar en ello mientras va en busca de otro trapo."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1562
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_f5db778b:

    # "He winds up heading to the tennis courts, because he knows there's a cleaning cupboard in the building where the changing rooms are."
    "Termina yendo a las canchas de tenis, porque sabe que hay un armario en el edificio donde están los vestidores."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1563
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_4f68f2b5:

    # "So Kyou steps inside, takes a new cloth..."
    "Así que Kyou entra, toma un trapo..."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1566
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_3bce9ac6:

    # "But as he comes out of there he finds Risa following him out. She had been in the girl's changing room doing cleaning apparently."
    "Pero al salir se encuentra con Risa. Al parecer ella estaba limpiando en los vestidores."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1568
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_1c888721:

    # "She loudly demands to know what the hell Kyou was doing in the girl's changing rooms." with dissolve
    "Ruidosamente, exige saber qué diablos está haciendo Kyou en los vestidores de chicas." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1569
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_31a93f74:

    # "As Kyou protests, Risa's loud accusation arouses the attention of several other students, who start bringing up the rumours about Kyou being a predatory creep."
    "Kyou protesta, y las escandalosas acusaciones de Risa atraen la atención de otros estudiantes, quienes empiezan a hablar de los rumores de que Kyou es un predador."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1570
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_94d4c3e8:

    # "Kyou's attempts to explain himself fall on deaf ears as Risa frisks him."
    "Los intentos de Kyou por explicarse son ignorados mientras Risa lo examina."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1571
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_2d6ddf96:

    # r frown "Well, isn't that something..." with dissolve
    r frown "Vaya, ¿qué tenemos aquí?..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1572
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_8774da5f:

    # "Kyou's heart stops as Risa seemingly pulls out a pair of girl's panties from Kyou's pocket in front of everyone."
    "El corazón de Kyou se detiene cuando Risa, al parecer, saca un par de pantaletas de dama del bolcillo de Kyou delante de todos."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1573
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_e76cc454:

    # "While Kyou is left speechless, Risa demands that enough is enough and it's time for Kyou to answer for his crimes..."
    "Kyou se queda sin habla, y Risa exclama que ya es suficiente, y que es hora de que Kyou pague por sus crímenes..."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1575
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_6334c7c7:

    # "Next, we see Kyou hauled in front of the principal, along with several other students..."
    "Posteriormente vemos a Kyou transportado a la oficina del director, junto con algunos estudiantes más..."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1578
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_403f0c81:

    # "Risa is called on to speak first." with dissolve
    "Risa es la primera en recibir la palabra." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1579
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_e925268d:

    # "She reveals that Hiroko had talked to her privately about her gym clothes getting rifled through and her change of panties going missing."
    "Revela que Hiroko le ha dicho en privado que alguien ha escarbado entre su ropa de gimnasio y que sus pantaletas extra han estado desapareciendo."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1580
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_b2171545:

    # "Hiroko suspected Kyou was the culprit, but she had no proof it was him until now and was afraid no one of authority would take her seriously, so she kept quiet."
    "Hiroko sospechaba que Kyou era el culpable, pero no tenía pruebas hasta ahora, y temía que ninguna autoridad la tomara en serio, así que se quedó callada."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1581
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_34fc526a:

    # "That's also why Risa had an eye out for suspicious behaviour, and immediately noticed something was up when she noticed Kyou in the changing room area."
    "Es también por eso que Risa había estado buscando comportamiento sospechoso, e inmediatamente noto que algo ocurría cuando vio a Kyou cerca de los vestidores."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1584
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_03dcc5c6:

    # "Sayori is next to speak, as she notes how Kyou and Hiroko have long been feuding in the classroom." with dissolve
    "Sayori es la siguiente en hablar, denotando la enemistad que Kyou y Hiroko an tenido en el aula." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1585
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_83b11b6d:

    # "She points out that their confrontations died down in recent months, but came back with a vengeance as Hiroko neared the time of her critical tennis tournement."
    "Señaló que sus confrontaciones se habían reducido los últimos meses, pero regresaron poco antes de su crítico torneo de tenis. "

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1587
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_e3e8e049:

    # "The panty thefts are proof that Kyou has escalated his dangerous obsession with her." with dissolve
    "El robo de pantaletas son prueba de que Kyou ha escalado su peligrosa obsesión con ella." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1588
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_c1f6761e:

    # "There's no doubt his harassment has had a devastating effect on Hiroko's state of mind and that Kyou is only going to escalate further until he is stopped."
    "No hay duda de que su acoso ha tenido un efecto devastador en el estado mental de Hiroko y de que Kyou no hará más que seguir escalando hasta no ser detenido."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1591
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_de718637:

    # "Nozomi is up next, speaking on behalf of both herself and Hiroko, as she corroborates Risa's story." with dissolve
    "Luego es turno de Nozomi, hablando tanto en su nombre como en el de Hiroko, corroborando la historia de Risa." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1592
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_af73e122:

    # "Hiroko confided in her about the panty thefts as well, and her fears about not being taken seriously by anyone with the power to do anything."
    "Hiroko también le contó lo de los robos de pantaletas, y su miedo de no ser tomada en serio por nadie con el poder de hacer nada."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1594
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_ea83f502:

    # "Nozomi goes on to say that Kyou's frequent bullying and harrassment is why Hiroko broke down at the tennis tournament this weekend. It's all because of him!" with dissolve
    "Nozomi continúa y dice que el frecuente abuso y acoso de Kyou es la razón por la cual Hiroko se debilitó en el torneo de tenis del fin de semana pasado." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1595
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_d4838399:

    # "She hopes for the sake of her friend that now the harrassment has taken a sexual nature that the school will take action for Hiroko's sake."
    "Ella espera, por el bien de su amiga, que ahora que el acoso es de naturaleza sexual, la escuela tome acción para ayudar a Hiroko."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1597
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_6ec21458:

    # "And what does Kyou have to say for himself?"
    "¿Y qué es lo que Kyou tiene que decir?"

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1598
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_8d7c15a0:

    # "Kyou... admits it's true. He's resented Hiroko for years and wanted to take her down a peg, so he kept picking on her."
    "Kyou... admite que es cierto. Ha resentido a Hiroko por años y quería bajarle los humos, así que fue contra ella."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1599
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_c96a6eab:

    # "And recently, yeah, he started sneaking into the changing rooms during cleaning time and stealing her panties."
    "Y recientemente, sí, comenzó a escabullirse a los vestidores durante la limpieza para robar sus pantaletas."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1600
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_365d4c8f:

    # "The principal finds it refreshing that Kyou is giving a straight confession instead of wasting even more of his time, and dismisses the girls."
    "Al director le parece refrescante que Kyou esté dando una confesión directa, en lugar de hacerlo perder más tiempo, y deja que las chicas se retiren."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1601
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_2334467d:

    # "After they leave, the principal informs Kyou that he's issuing him with a suspension, pending further review by the school board where he'll likely be expelled."
    "Una vez se han ido, el director le confirma a Kyou lo sancionará con una suspensión, y queda pendiente una revisión adicional en la junta directiva de la escuela donde es probable que sea expulsado."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1602
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_3a8c93fe:

    # "There'll be arrangements for him to take his entrance exams at home should that happen, but regardless, this incident will leave a mark on his record."
    "Lo acomodarán para que haga sus exámenes de admisión en casa, si es que ocurre, pero a pesar de eso, este incidente dejará una marca en su registro."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1603
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_682674c7:

    # "The principal asks if Kyou understands the severity of the situation, and Kyou says he does. Then he's dismissed."
    "El director pregunta si Kyou entiende la seriedad de la situación, y Kyou dice que sí. Luego le permite retirarse."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1605
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_196af540:

    # "Kyou trudges homeward, feeling extremely shaken up."
    "Kyou se va, sintiéndose extremadamente agitado."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1606
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_14003040:

    # "He doesn't know what to think of what happened back there..."
    "No sabe qué pensar de lo que sucedió ahí..."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1608
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_e8fb78ef:

    # "But instead of going home, he heads for the shopping district in town, and enters a karaoke bar."
    "Pero en lugar de irse a casa, se va al distrito comercial de la ciudad, y entra a un bar de karaoke."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1610
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_29fb8480:

    # "He drops his name at the desk, and they direct him to a room where he's expected..."
    "Dice su nombre en la recepción y lo dirigen a una habitación donde lo esperan..."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1618
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_0e4b1448:

    # "And finds his accusers waiting for him."
    "Y encuentra a sus acusadoras aguardando a su llegada."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1619
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_6ab632f4:

    # "Kyou thanks everyone for helping to enact his plan, in case the reader hadn't twigged by now what was going on here."
    "Kyou les agradece a todas por seguir su plan, en caso de que el lector no haya descifrado ya lo que estaba ocurriendo."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1620
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_d62f2aaa:

    # "The group has some mixed feelings about what they participated in today."
    "El grupo tiene sentimientos mixtos por lo que hicieron hoy."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1622
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_fe946614:

    # "Risa only did it to help her friend get some justice, but it leaves a bad taste in her mouth to frame Kyou for something he didn't do." with dissolve
    "Risa solo lo hizo para ayudar a que su amiga recibiera justicia, pero le deja un mal sabor de boca culpar a Kyou por algo que no hizo." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1624
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_099f001c:

    # "Sayori concedes that it felt insane to go along with it, but..." with dissolve
    "Sayori reconoce que ser partícipe de esto se sintió como una locura, pero..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1625
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_5bf330fb:

    # "This was Kyou's plan, after all."
    "Este fue el plan de Kyou, después de todo."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1627
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_657b5f9a:

    # "Sayori believes the school board will accept the extenuating circumstances surrounding Hiroko's preparation for the tournament as a reason for her failure to distinguish herself." with dissolve
    "Sayori cree que la junta directiva de la escuela aceptará las extenuantes circunstancias en torno a la preparación de Hiroko para el torneo como la razón de su fracaso en destacar." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1628
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_1430625a:

    # "Hiroko will get another chance, she's sure of it."
    "Hiroko recibirá otra oportunidad, está segura."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1630
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_7f585e16:

    # "But is Kyou really okay with destroying his immediate future for the chance of saving Hiroko's? Nozomi supposes it's far too late to consider now..." with dissolve
    "Pero ¿en verdad está Kyou dispuesto a destruir su futuro inmediato por la oportunidad de salvar el de Hiroko? Nozomi supone que ya es muy tarde para considerarlo..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1632
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_8d5796f8:

    # "Kyou is committed to this, Sayori agrees. She never thought he had it in him. And she takes back what she said about him being \"irredeemable filth.\". For what it's worth." with dissolve
    "Kyou se ha comprometido a esto, concuerda Sayori. Nunca pensó que sería capaz. Y se retractó de llamarlo una \"irredimible escoria\". Si sirve de algo." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1633
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_c203d210:

    # "She just hopes Kyou is prepared to face the consequences of his actions here."
    "Solo espera que Kyou esté preparado para enfrentar las consecuencias de sus actos."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1634
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_b8867653:

    # "Kyou confirms he knows what he's doing. But he hurt Hiroko badly and this is the only way to sincerely make amends."
    "Kyou confirma que sabe lo que hace. Pero le hizo mucho daño a Hiroko y esta es la única manera de enmendarlo."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1638
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_f15dbf05:

    # "Sayori respects Kyou's bravery in seeing this through, then sternly reminds the others that they need to keep the masquerade going." with dissolve
    "Sayori respeta el valor de Kyou, luego les recuerda a todos severamente que deben mantener la mascarada." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1639
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_2d3c13ec:

    # "Only the five of them, Hiroko included, know the true story."
    "Solo ellos cinco, Hiroko incluida, conocen la verdadera historia."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1640
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_16b6e90a:

    # "If word gets out to the faculty that this scandal was fabricated they could all be in trouble and Kyou's sacrifice will have been for nothing."
    "Si se llega a saber en la facultad que este escándalo fue orquestado, todos podrían meterse en problemas, y el sacrificio de Kyou habrá sido en vano."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1642
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_48905d6e:

    # "As for Kyou, she sincerely wishes him luck for the future. If he needs some help with his entrance exams, she may be able to offer some guidance." with dissolve
    "En cuanto a Kyou, sinceramente le desea suerte en su porvenir. Si necesita ayuda en sus exámenes de admisión, podría ofrecerle algo de orientación." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1643
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_50399290:

    # "But that pretty much concludes the meeting of this most awkward of alliances."
    "Pero eso básicamente concluye la reunión de esta incómoda alianza."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1644
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_a794495b:

    # "Will someone dare suggest singing a round of karaoke while they're in here? No?"
    "¿Se atreverá alguien a sugerir cantar karaoke ya que están aquí? ¿No?"

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1647
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_693d66b7:

    # "Kyou returns home soon after."
    "Kyou regresa a casa poco después."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1648
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_024e2a8b:

    # "He gave up so much trying to set things right, but was it all in vain?"
    "Sacrificó mucho intentando arreglar las cosas, pero ¿habrás sido en vano? "

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1649
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_152605a0:

    # "Right now there's no way to know, and his selfless act doesn't make the pain he's been through any easier."
    "Ahora mismo no hay manera de saber, y su acto de altruismo no calma ni un poco el dolor por el que ha pasado."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1650
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_2eb7ca5c:

    # "What's going to happen to Hiroko now?"
    "¿Qué le pasará ahora a Hiroko?"

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1651
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_f9aa11bd:

    # "... What's going to happen to Kyou?"
    "... ¿Qué le pasará a Kyou?"

# TODO: Translation updated at 2020-12-09 00:38

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1543
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_446c933e:

    # "It's been a rough few days since that night."
    "Han pasado algunos días muy duros desde esa noche."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1544
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_ff15e52d:

    # "Using the penlight wasn't going to make things better, and smashing it to pieces didn't magically help anyone."
    "Usar la linterna no iba a mejorar las cosas, y hacerla pedazos no ayudó mágicamente a nadie."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1546
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_71f2a729:

    # "But... I have a plan."
    "Pero... tengo un plan."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1548
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_5b0c2081:

    # "A stupid... desperate... maybe even suicidal plan..."
    "Un plan estúpido... desesperado... tal vez incluso suicida..."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1549
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_4eadbebf:

    # "I feel a lump in my throat just thinking about it, but if I really want to make up for what I did, I'll see it though."
    "Siento un nudo en la garganta de solo pensarlo, pero si en verdad quiero enmendar lo que hice, tengo que hacerlo."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:3534
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_3f7a33e8:

    # "I feel a lump in my throat just thinking about it, but if I really want to make up for what I did, I'll see it through."
    "Siento un nudo en la garganta de solo pensarlo, pero si en verdad quiero enmendar lo que hice, tengo que hacerlo."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1550
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_ca11396e:

    # "This is the best I can do, Hiroko..."
    "Esto es lo mejor que puedo hacer, Hiroko..."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1552
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_b6fcbcbe:

    # "First, I still have to show up for class."
    "Primero debo ir a clase."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1553
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_ee43c95b:

    # "People scarcely even look my way anymore. The whole room's got this uncomfortable air of resentment caused by my very presence in it."
    "La gente ya casi ni me mira. La habitación está llena de un incómodo aire de resentimiento causado por mi mera presencia."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1557
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_a3014bad:

    # a "Morning, everyone." with dissolve
    a "Buenos días a todos." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1558
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_0cd5571b:

    # "Not even Akiko really acknowledges me anymore."
    "Ni siquiera Akiko me dirige la palabra."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1559
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_91619809:

    # r "Yeah. Morning."
    r "Sí. Buenos días."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1562
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_5f5c59c0:

    # "But I've got more important things to worry about. Like getting through the day." with dissolve
    "Pero tengo cosas más importantes de las que preocuparme. Como sobrevivir el día." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1563
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_7cbc4d96:

    # "Just gotta go through the motions until school is out..."
    "Solo debo seguir la rutina hasta que la escuela termine..."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1568
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_6a707771:

    # "It both helps and hurts that no one bothers me."
    "Que nadie me moleste es tan conveniente como doloroso."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1569
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_0fd8f788:

    # "I go through my day. I eat lunch alone. I sit through the lessons..."
    "Sigo con mi día. Almuerzo a solas. Escucho las lecciones..."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1570
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_d703a287:

    # "The loneliness gnaws at me but I'll endure, knowing how getting people's attention just makes things so much worse for me..."
    "La soledad me carcome, pero voy a aguantar, sabiendo que atraer la atención de la gente solo empeora las cosas para mí..."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1573
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_e38556e1:

    # "Eventually, the day passes and cleaning time arrives."
    "Eventualmente, la jornada concluye y llega la hora de la limpieza."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1574
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_894912c3:

    # "Just a little left to go..."
    "Solo un poco más..."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1576
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_d93fd2df:

    # "I'm cleaning the corridor today, along with a couple others."
    "Hoy me toca limpiar el pasillo, junto con algunas personas más."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1578
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_b0d6f82f:

    # "Akiko being one of them." with dissolve
    "Entre ellas, Akiko." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1579
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_a3e606ac:

    # "That conversation we had last time we were on cleaning duty together... It almost feels like a year ago."
    "Aquella conversación que tuvimos la última vez que limpiamos juntos... Casi se siente que fue hace un año."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1580
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_a1d5afbe:

    # "She's in no mood for talking this time, so I'll... hmm..."
    "No está de humor para hablar esta vez, así que voy a... mmm..."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1581
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_e9d9076d:

    # ks frown "Ugh, this is no good."
    ks frown "Aj, esto no sirve."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1582
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_f06ea264:

    # a uniform armband neutral "Uh, what is?" with dissolve
    a uniform armband neutral "Eh, ¿qué cosa?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1583
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_7f95834e:

    # "Akiko talks to me, but her tone suggests this time it's all business."
    "Akiko me habla, pero su tono sugiere que, esta vez, es solo por trabajo."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1584
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_258d960d:

    # ks sigh "This cleaning cloth's ragged. I need a new one."
    ks sigh "Este trapo está muy harapiento. Necesito uno nuevo."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1586
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_f732ba00:

    # a sleep "Oh..." with dissolve
    a sleep "Oh..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1588
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_9744b5e5:

    # a "Well. I guess you'd better get a new one, then." with dissolve
    a "Bueno. Supongo que será mejor que consigas uno." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1589
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_b7f91a2b:

    # a neutral "Just hurry back." with dissolve
    a neutral "Pero date prisa." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1591
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_3f0ad8a2:

    # "It stings, hearing Akiko so dismissive. But it's all I expected."
    "Duele oír a Akiko tan despectiva. Pero no esperaba otra cosa."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1592
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_5fb24dfc:

    # "Risa must have really gotten to her the other day."
    "Risa debe haberla afectado mucho el otro día."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1594
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_59450ede:

    # "Anyway, I head outside and walk across the tennis courts."
    "Como sea, salgo y camino hasta las canchas de tenis."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1595
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_d7e5e049:

    # "Maybe I could've asked one of the other groups if they brought a spare, but I know the changing rooms down here have a cleaning cupboard."
    "Tal vez pude preguntarle a uno de los otros grupos si tenía alguno de sobra, pero sé que estos vestidores tienen un almacén de limpieza."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1596
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_a43d4d2a:

    # "I'll get a new cloth from there."
    "Sacaré un trapo nuevo de ahí."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1601
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_f7ddbc43:

    # "Let's see... yep, I didn't even need to ask someone to unlock it. I'll just help myself to one, then."
    "A ver... sip, ni siquiera tuve que pedirle a alguien que lo abriera. Solo tomaré uno."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1603
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_1f4da55d:

    # "And now I better rush back before I piss people off even more- {w=1.5}{nw}"
    "Y ahora será mejor que me apresure antes de hacer enfadar más a la gen-{w=1.5}"

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1604
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_ae551dbf:

    # r "{size=30}Kyou! What are you doing back here?{/size}"
    r "{size=30}¡Kyou! ¿Qué haces aquí atrás?{/size}"

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1609
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_11ffd01e:

    # "What? Risa?"
    "¿Qué? ¿Risa?"

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1610
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_1bd25898:

    # ks surprised "Huh? I was just- {w=0.5}{nw}"
    ks surprised "¿Eh? Solo estaba- {w=0.5}{nw}"

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1612
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_81124a9f:

    # r frown "{size=30}You're not supposed to be back here!{/size}" with dissolve
    r frown "{size=30}¡No deberías estar aquí atrás!{/size}" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1613
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_e6d95706:

    # "She must have been cleaning in the changing rooms and followed me out when she noticed me. This could get ugly..."
    "Debe haber estado limpiando en los vestidores y me siguió cuando me vio. Esto podría ponerse feo..."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1614
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_4962fe41:

    # ks sigh "I-I'm only here to get another cloth, see? Leave me alone."
    ks sigh "S-solo vine por un trapo, ¿ves? Déjame en paz."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1615
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_7b4e85eb:

    # r uniform "{size=30}Not buying it, Kyou. Not today. You're up to something.{/size}" with dissolve
    r uniform "{size=30}No te creo, Kyou. Hoy no. Traes algo entre manos.{/size}" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1616
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_8f25fd21:

    # "She's talking loudly. Accusingly. And it's getting people's attention."
    "Está hablando muy fuerte. Con tono acusatorio. Y está atrayendo la atención de la gente."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1618
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_6d75f38f:

    # t "Hey, isn't that Koyama?"
    t "Oye, ¿qué no es Koyama?"

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1619
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_b9697f84:

    # "There's more people coming out of the changing rooms, and some others are staring at us from inside the main school building."
    "Más personas empiezan a salir de los vestidores, y algunas otras nos miran desde el interior del edificio principal de la escuela."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1621
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_472c77d3:

    # t "Just looking at that guy gives me the creeps."
    t "Ese chico me da escalofríos de solo verlo."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1622
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_9572f392:

    # "Shit. That's a lot of attention..."
    "Mierda. Es mucha atención..."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1624
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_ddff763f:

    # t "What do you think he's doing?"
    t "¿Qué crees que esté haciendo?"

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1625
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_158747c6:

    # ks surprised "I'm... I-I'm not doing ANYTHING!"
    ks surprised "¡No... N-no estoy haciendo NADA!"

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1626
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_922b58ca:

    # "I can't even leave, as more and more people start to gather around."
    "Ni siquiera puedo irme, pues más y más gente comienza a acumularse a nuestro alrededor."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1628
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_29aac6d5:

    # "A-and just then I'm startled as I feel Risa's hands in my pockets!" with vpunch
    "¡Y d-de pronto me toman por sorpresa las manos de Risa, entrando a mis bolcillos!" with vpunch

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1629
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_28c84075:

    # ks "R-RISA!"
    ks "¡R-RISA!"

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1631
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_1d97cd76:

    # "But what's more shocking is when she pulls her hand away from me, gripping something tightly between her fingers." with dissolve
    "Pero lo más impactante de todo es cuando me quita la mano de encima, agarrando algo fuertemente entre sus dedos." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1632
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_bffe1a7b:

    # "It's enough for the people crowded around us to briefly stop in their tracks when they spy what she's holding."
    "Eso provoca que la gente que no rodea se detenga brevemente para espiar lo que está sujetando."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1633
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_28f0bfdb:

    # r angry "Well, isn't that something..." with dissolve
    r angry "Vaya, ¿qué tenemos aquí...?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1636
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_d9540625:

    # t "{size=30}P-P-...{w=1.0}{/size}{nw}"
    t "{size=30}¡¿P-P...{w=1.0}{/size}{nw}"

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1637
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_73b6b514:

    # extend "{size=30} PANTIES?!{/size}" with vpunch
    extend "{size=30} PANTALETAS?!{/size}" with vpunch

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1640
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_ad961c60:

    # "The gathering crowd were already agitated, but now they're starting to turn violent as I feel someone shove me from the side." with vpunch
    "La multitud ya estaba agitada, pero ahora comienza a ponerse violenta, y siento cómo alguien me empuja desde el costado." with vpunch

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1641
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_7fc966d4:

    # "Meanwhile, Risa hoists those panties in the air for everyone assembled to see."
    "Mientras tanto, Risa alza la ropa interior en alto, para que todo el mundo la vea."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1642
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_6a18cbdf:

    # r "{size=30}What's it going to take to get this guy out of here, huh? How long's he going to keep getting away with harassing us?{/size}"
    r "{size=30}¿Qué hace falta para sacar a este chico de aquí, eh? ¿Cuánto más podrá acosarnos y salirse con la suya?{/size}"

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:3628
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_0f0363bc:

    # r "{size=30}What's it going to take to get this guy out of here, huh?{/size}"
    r "{size=30}¿Qué hace falta para sacar a este chico de aquí, eh?{/size}"

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:3629
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_266e71c4:

    # r "{size=30}How long's he going to keep getting away with harassing us?{/size}"
    r "{size=30}¿Cuánto más podrá acosarnos y salirse con la suya?{/size}"

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1643
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_b3b07cd8:

    # r angry_side "{size=30}I say enough is {/size}{nw}" with dissolve
    r angry_side "{size=30}¡Yo digo que ya es {/size}{nw}" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1644
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_99351545:

    # extend "{size=40}ENOUGH!{/size}" with vpunch
    extend "{size=40}SUFICIENTE!{/size}" with vpunch

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1645
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_0e56efd3:

    # ks surprised "H-hey WAIT A SEC!"
    ks surprised "¡O-oigan, UN SEGUNDO!"

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1647
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_d606e1bb:

    # "... But my words come to nothing as I'm drowned out in a chorus of angry shouting while I'm pushed to and fro."
    "... Pero mis palabras se ahogan junto conmigo en un coro de iracundos gritos mientras soy empujado de un lado a otro."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1648
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_91645d48:

    # "I'm lucky there were a couple teachers around to break things up before someone threw a punch."
    "Tuve suerte que hubiera un par de profesores cerca que le pusieron un alto antes de que alguien usara los puños."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1656
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_21483842:

    # "... Although as I stand here half an hour later, in the principal's office, it's hard to think of myself as fortunate."
    "... Aunque, estando aquí parado media hora después, en la oficina del director, es difícil considerarme afortunado."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1658
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_3f9e2fd5:

    # t "Kyou Koyama..."
    t "Kyou Koyama..."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1659
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_86606079:

    # ks surprised "S-... Sir?"
    ks surprised "¿S-... Señor?"

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1660
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_65649d38:

    # "The principal himself sits at his desk, looking disdainfully my way as I stand anxiously on the other side, along with a few of my current and former classmates."
    "El director se sienta en su escritorio, mirando con desdén en mi dirección, mientras yo aguardo del otro lado con ansiedad, junto a algunas de mis actuales y antiguas compañeras."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1662
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_fb83a94d:

    # t "There's a name I was not expecting to hear again so quickly. And yet, here we are."
    t "Un nombre que no esperaba volver a oír tan pronto. Y sin embargo, henos aquí."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1663
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_052aac6a:

    # "Inhaling sharply, he then mercifully turns his attention towards one of said classmates."
    "Inhalando con brusquedad, piadosamente dirige su atención a una de las ya mencionadas compañeras."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1664
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_b8ca369b:

    # t "Now I understand you apprehended the... *sigh* panty thief."
    t "Pues bien, por lo que entiendo usted aprendió al... *suspiro* ladón de pantaletas."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1666
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_a4ef8ce1:

    # r "Yes, Sir. I tailed him after I caught him sneaking into the changing rooms." with dissolve
    r "Sí, Señor. Lo seguí cuando lo atrapé escabulléndose en los vestidores." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1668
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_38b9d4d9:

    # "She shoots a sideways glance at me before she continues." with dissolve
    "Me da una mirada de soslayo antes de continuar." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1669
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_5ef79f53:

    # r frown_side "They were right there in his pocket. I knew he was up to something like this." with dissolve
    r frown_side "Estaban justo ahí en su bolcillo. Sabía que tramaba algo como esto." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1670
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_0bdef9c3:

    # t "Do you now, Tachibana? You're someone else I've had to hear about all too recently."
    t "¿De verdad, Tachibana? De usted también he escuchado mucho recientemente."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1671
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_806ab1c1:

    # r uniform_armup concerned_side "Ah... y-yeah, I mean..." with dissolve
    r uniform_armup concerned_side "Ah... s-sí, bueno..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1673
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_90520344:

    # "Another glance my way..." with dissolve
    "Otra mirada en mi dirección..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1944
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_e979e81b:

    # r uniform concerned_side "My friend Hiroko, in class 3-B, she... s-she was telling me someone had been going through her gym clothes and taking her change of underwear." with dissolve
    r uniform concerned_side "Mi amiga Hiroko, de la clase 3-B, me... m-me dijo que alguien había estado escarbando entre su ropa de gimnasio y robando su cambio de ropa interior." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1675
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_25bb22aa:

    # r sleeptalk "It started happening since the day Kyou got transferred, so she thought it had to be him, but we couldn't prove it before now." with dissolve
    r sleeptalk "Comenzó a ocurrir desde el día que Kyou fue transferido, así que pensó que debía ser él, pero no habíamos podido probarlo hasta ahora." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1676
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_d96c67f5:

    # t "And did either of you relay these specific concerns to a member of staff?"
    t "¿Y alguna de ustedes le comunicó estas preocupaciones en particular a algún miembro del personal?"

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1678
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_1fbf8bdc:

    # "Risa seems to tense up under the question, but after a pause she has an answer for him." with dissolve
    "Risa parece tensarse ante la pregunta, pero tras una pausa, tiene una respuesta para él." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1679
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_c382ba0a:

    # r uniform_armup concerned_side "No, Sir. Hiroko told me no one would take it seriously anyway so she thought it'd be more trouble than it was worth." with dissolve
    r uniform_armup concerned_side "No, Señor. Hiroko me dijo que nadie la tomaría en serio de todos modos, así que pensó que no valía la pena molestarse." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1680
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_0e765fa5:

    # r neutral_side "But yeah, that's why I found it suspicious when Kyou came wandering into those changing rooms." with dissolve
    r neutral_side "Pero sí, por eso me pareció sospechoso ver a Kyou deambulando junto a los vestidores." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1681
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_13e8d3a6:

    # r frown "And I was right." with dissolve
    r frown "Y tenía razón." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1682
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_72576aa7:

    # t "That will do, Tachibana."
    t "Con eso basta, Tachibana."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1684
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_e810d348:

    # "As Risa steps back, our principal centers his gaze on another of my accusers." with dissolve
    "Risa da un paso atrás y nuestro director centra su mirada en otra de las acusadoras." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1685
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_4cfc97d6:

    # t "Watanabe. You had something to say?"
    t "Watanabe. ¿Tiene algo que decir?"

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1693
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_f4966e54:

    # s "I do, Sir." with dissolve
    s "Sí, Señor." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1694
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_2a4f4338:

    # "Yeah, Sayori. After the ruckus, Risa told them this was about Hiroko and that her friends should be consulted."
    "Sí, Sayori. Después del alboroto, Risa les dijo que esto era sobre Hiroko y que sus amigas debían ser consultadas."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1695
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_5c750d2a:

    # s neutral "I am not sure if you are aware, but before his transfer, Kyou and Hiroko had a history of feuding in the classroom; dating back to our time as first years." with dissolve
    s neutral "No sé si está enterado, pero previo a la transferencia, Kyou y Hiroko tenían un historial de enemistad en el aula; el cual se remonta a primer año." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1696
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_23c59650:

    # s uniform_folded concerned "I am afraid it was only a matter of time before he escalated his behaviour and committed some serious harm." with dissolve
    s uniform_folded concerned "Me temo que solo fue cuestión de tiempo para que escalara su comportamiento y causara algún daño severo." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1697
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_1f928c13:

    # s annoyed "And as you have now seen, removing him from our classroom did nothing to abate his dangerous obsession with her." with dissolve
    s annoyed "Y como ya ha visto, removerlo de nuestro salón no hizo nada por amainar su peligrosa obsesión con ella." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1698
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_f2e912bc:

    # s irritated "Indeed, robbed of the ability to harass her during class, Kyou simply became more creative in his efforts to hurt Hiroko." with dissolve
    s irritated "En efecto, despojado de la habilidad de acosarla durante las clases, Kyou simplemente fue más creativo en sus esfuerzos por herir a Hiroko." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1699
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_9366d9c9:

    # s uniform annoyed "And it is my opinion that he will continue these escalations even further if he is not stopped." with dissolve
    s uniform annoyed "Y opino que tan solo continuará escalando hasta no ser detenido." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1700
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_fabbb1c0:

    # t "Yes, Watanabe, your opinion is duly noted."
    t "Sí, Watanabe, su opinión será tomada en cuenta."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1701
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_7049ff08:

    # "He speaks disdainfully, but I have to wonder why he let her mouth off about me for as long as that if he didn't care for her opinion."
    "Habla desdeñosamente, pero me preguntó por qué la dejó hablar tanto de mí si no le importaba su opinión."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1703
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_81aacdab:

    # t "And you... Akemi, is it?" with dissolve
    t "Y usted... Akemi, ¿cierto?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1714
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_9a312310:

    # n "Y- yes, Sir." with dissolve
    n "S- sí, Señor." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1715
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_8ca2d670:

    # t "Why is Homura not with you?"
    t "¿Por qué Homura no se encuentra con ustedes?"

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1716
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_519d9b8f:

    # n sad_side "She..." with dissolve
    n sad_side "Ella..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1717
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_74ba2918:

    # "Yeah, Nozomi's here too. Still as nervous as I've seen her lately."
    "Sí, Nozomi también está aquí. Y sigue tan nerviosa como la he visto últimamente."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1718
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_735a221f:

    # n sad_closed "Hiroko doesn't want to be in the same room as him." with dissolve
    n sad_closed "Hiroko no quiere estar en la misma habitación que él." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1719
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_9bd665f8:

    # t "Understood. Now, do you have anything to add?"
    t "Entendido. Entonces, ¿tiene algo que añadir?"

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1720
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_52097f56:

    # n sad_side "Yes. I... um, I wanted to corroborate what Risa said, about Hiroko having her panties stolen. She told me as well." with dissolve
    n sad_side "Sí. Yo... em, quería corroborar lo que Risa dijo, sobre ropa interior robada de Hiroko. A mí también me lo contó." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1721
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_26cbc4b6:

    # n sad_closed "And all this has really gotten to her, Sir. What Kyou did to make her life a misery... i-it's unforgivable." with dissolve
    n sad_closed "Y todo esto la ha afectado mucho, Señor. Lo que Kyou hizo para hacer su vida miserable... e-es imperdonable." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1722
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_a3bccf05:

    # n sad "So I hope..." with dissolve
    n sad "Así que espero..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1723
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_1e6aa7c1:

    # n frown "I-I hope this school does the right thing and gets this sexual harrassor out of our lives for good!" with dissolve
    n frown "¡E-espero que la escuela haga lo correcto y saque a este acosador sexual de nuestras vidas de una vez!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1725
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_180f1508:

    # "Our principal sighs and holds a hand to his head." with dissolve
    "Nuestro director suspira y se lleva una mano a la cabeza." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1726
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_d95f7a29:

    # t "I've heard enough. Girls, please go about your day. You are dismissed."
    t "Ya oí suficiente. Chicas, por favor regresen a sus asuntos. Pueden retirarse."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1728
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_f5cd8d3d:

    # "The room falls silent for a moment as my three accusers bow stiffly to the principal before seeing themselves out."
    "La habitación queda en silencio por un momento, en lo que mis tres acusadoras hacen una rígida reverencia antes de salir."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1729
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_f4bc7e6f:

    # "Leaving me alone with this guy."
    "Dejándome a solas con este sujeto."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1736
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_40d69371:

    # t "So, Koyama. What do you have to say for yourself?"
    t "Entonces, Koyama. ¿Qué es lo que tiene que decir?"

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1737
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_5e12dd5d:

    # ks "I..."
    ks "Yo..."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1738
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_d1f9c7b7:

    # "What do I have to say?"
    "¿Qué tengo que decir?"

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1739
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_a83048ba:

    # ks neutral "Uh..."
    ks neutral "Eh..."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1740
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_38b75ebc:

    # "Even if I could talk my way out of this, why would I want to anymore?"
    "Aunque pudiera salir de esta, ¿por qué querría?"

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1741
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_3cc25fd0:

    # ks sigh "It's true, Sir."
    ks sigh "Es cierto, Señor."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1742
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_7561f938:

    # "My school life's already turned to shit, no matter the outcome here."
    "Mi vida escolar ya se convirtió en mierda, no importa en qué resulte esto."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1743
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_abe839c4:

    # ks frown "I've hated Hiroko since we were first years. She's always mouthing off about me being a creep or something stupid like that. It pissed me off."
    ks frown "He odiado a Hiroko desde primer año. Se la pasa diciendo que soy un bicho raro o alguna estupidez así. Me sacaba de quicio."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1744
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_cc9e2f61:

    # ks "S-so yeah, I wanted to knock her off her perch, you know?"
    ks "A-así que, sí, quería bajarle un poco los humos, ya sabe."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1745
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_b72e6eff:

    # "I'll be the creep they all think me to be."
    "Seré el bicho que todos ven en mí."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1746
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_a0420d3f:

    # ks "Maybe I took it too far with the panty-stealing thing, huh."
    ks "Tal vez fui muy lejos con lo de la ropa interior, ¿no?"

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1747
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_3a0993fb:

    # t "Well... I find it refreshing that you are not wasting even more of my time by attempting to deny what you've done."
    t "Bueno... Me parece refrescante que no me esté haciendo perder más tiempo intentando negar lo que has hecho."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:3959
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_0c3b7f3b:

    # t "But as administrator of this school I cannot overlook this brazen act of harassment upon another student."
    t "Pero como el administrador de esta escuela, no puedo pasar por alto este acto descarado de acoso hacia otra estudiante."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1749
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_ab23eaa1:

    # t "I therefore have no other choice but to issue you with an immediate suspension, pending further review by the school board."
    t "Por lo tanto no tengo más opción que sancionarte con una suspensión, y queda pendiente una revisión por la junta directiva de la escuela."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1750
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_f08ef1b1:

    # t "But I can assure you, Koyama, that this will be a formality. The board will recommend your expulsion."
    t "Pero puedo asegurarle, Koyama, que esto será una formalidad. La junta directiva recomendará su expulsión."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:3740
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_91b99dad:

    # t "Do you understand the severity of your situation now, Koyama?"
    t "¿Entiende la seriedad de su situación, Koyama?"

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1752
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_28590c0e:

    # "I bow my head severely."
    "Inclino severamente la cabeza."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1753
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_f4b5bb2f:

    # ks "W-what about my entrance exams? Do I still get to take them?"
    ks "¿Qu-qué hay de mis exámenes de admisión? ¿Aún puedo tomarlos?"

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1754
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_d05edf14:

    # t "There will be arrangements for you to take the exams at home. But make no mistake, this will leave a mark on your record."
    t "Habrá un arreglo para que tome el examen desde casa. Pero no se confunda, esto dejará una marca en su registro."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1755
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_169692f4:

    # t "And that concludes our meeting, Koyama. We will not meet again."
    t "Y eso concluye nuestra reunión, Koyama. No volveremos a vernos."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1766
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_b2b88c02:

    # "I'm not sure I have any feeling left when I leave that place."
    "No sé si me queda algún sentimiento cuando salgo de ese lugar."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1768
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_bb4cb566:

    # "I don't even know what to think of what happened back there..."
    "Ni siquiera sé qué pensar de lo que pasó allá..."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1770
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_36524289:

    # "But I'm not going home just yet."
    "Pero aún no me voy a casa."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1771
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_e026754e:

    # "First I need to make a stop at one of the karaoke bars in town..."
    "Antes debo hacer una parada en uno de los bares de karaoke de la ciudad..."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1774
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_926cc385:

    # "I've never been in one of these places before, but all I have to do is go up to the counter and tell the clerk my name."
    "Nunca había estado en uno de estos lugares, pero solo tengo que ir al mostrador y decirle al encargado mi nombre."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1775
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_bad018b5:

    # "And they direct me to a room where I'm expected..."
    "Y me dirige a una sala donde me están esperando..."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1784
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_b242fe6e:

    # ks sigh "... Hey, everyone."
    ks sigh "... Hola a todas."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1785
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_f690e3cc:

    # s sleeptalk "Kyou." with dissolve
    s sleeptalk "Kyou." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1786
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_f261ace9:

    # "Yeah. This was always going to be weird."
    "Sí. Sabía que esto iba a ser raro."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1788
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_e142710c:

    # ks "U-uhh... thanks for everything back there." with dissolve
    ks "E-eeh... gracias por todo lo que hicieron." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1790
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_838778b5:

    # r concerned "You're welcome?" with dissolve
    r concerned "¿De nada?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:3890
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_68503ca5:

    # "Nozomi and Risa look to each other, seeming no more at ease now than they were back in the principal's office." with dissolve
    "Nozomi y Risa se miran la una a la otra, al parecer no más tranquilas de lo que estaban en la oficina del director." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1794
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_41f8372f:

    # r concerned "You know I wanted you punished for what you did to Hiro, but this doesn't feel like justice." with dissolve
    r concerned "Sabes que quería que te castigaran por lo que le hiciste a Hiro, pero esto no se siente justo." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1795
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_e42dd054:

    # n sad "Framing you for something like that... Was this really what you wanted, Kyou?" with dissolve
    n sad "Culparte de algo así... ¿Es esto en serio lo que querías, Kyou?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1796
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_3647356f:

    # "I shake my head ruefully."
    "Sacudo la cabeza con tristeza."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1797
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_50562c26:

    # ks "I didn't want any of this. But I wanted to help Hiroko come back from what I did to her. You know that, right?"
    ks "Yo no quería nada de esto. Pero quería ayudar a Hiroko a recuperarse de lo que le hice. Lo saben, ¿cierto?"

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1798
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_3eebc4da:

    # s uniform_folded concerned_right "Of course we know that. Even so, this plan of yours..." with dissolve
    s uniform_folded concerned_right "Desde luego que lo sabemos. Sin embargo, este plan..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1799
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_bda067f6:

    # "Yeah, Sayori. It was stupid, desperate and probably suicidal to my career prospects. I know."
    "Sí, Sayori, fue estúpido, desesperado y probablemente suicida para mis oportunidades de carrera. Lo sé."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1800
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_5b4fd328:

    # s sleeptalk_concerned "It felt insane to go along with it." with dissolve
    s sleeptalk_concerned "Seguirlo se sintió como una locura." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1806
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_2d559db9:

    # ks neutral "But you thought it would help, right?"
    ks neutral "Pero creías que ayudaría, ¿cierto? "

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1810
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_fc954ec5:

    # "Sayori nods." with dissolve
    "Sayori asiente." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1811
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_aa370b59:

    # s "And I still do. I believe if Hiroko submits an appeal to the scholarship board, they will take these extenuating circumstances into account."
    s "Y aún lo creo. Considero que, si Hiroko envía una apelación al consejo de becas, tomarán estas extenuantes circunstancias en cuenta."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1812
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_2d27ced8:

    # s concerned "There would be little doubt that your harassment contributed to Hiroko's mental decline and her failure to distinguish herself at the tournament." with dissolve
    s concerned "Pocas dudas habrá de que tu acoso contribuyó al declive mental de Hiroko y a su fracaso en destacar durante el torneo." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1813
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_c6f6b142:

    # s annoyed_right "Hiroko will get another chance, I have little doubt of that." with dissolve
    s annoyed_right "Hiroko recibirá otra oportunidad, de eso no me cabe duda." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1816
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_6735623e:

    # n side sad "That's good. But was it really okay for you to destroy your immediate future? Just for a chance to save Hiroko's?" with dissolve
    n side sad "Qué bueno. Pero ¿estuvo bien que destruyeras tu futuro inmediato? ¿Solo por una oportunidad de salvar el de Hiroko?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1817
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_780dadb9:

    # ks sigh "Well... I-it's too late for second-thoughts now, huh?"
    ks sigh "Bueno... ya es muy tarde para pensarlo dos veces, ¿no?"

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1818
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_a78a10af:

    # n sad_side "Yeah..." with dissolve
    n sad_side "Seh..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1821
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_fed084f2:

    # s uniform concerned "That's right. Kyou is fully committed to this reckless gambit, and we have committed to support him. For Hiroko." with dissolve
    s uniform concerned "Es correcto. Kyou se ha comprometido plenamente a esta osada jugada, y nosotras nos hemos comprometido a apoyarlo. Por Hiroko." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1822
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_fd7ddccd:

    # r uniform_armup concerned_side "Right. For Hiroko." with dissolve
    r uniform_armup concerned_side "Cierto. Por Hiroko." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1823
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_a85b7bb2:

    # s concerned_right "And for what it's worth, Kyou... I believe I owe you an apology." with dissolve
    s concerned_right "Y si sirve de algo, Kyou... Me parece que te debo una disculpa." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1826
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_b31dac94:

    # ks surprised "Huh?" with dissolve
    ks surprised "¿Eh?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1827
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_3e064102:

    # r frown_side "Yeah, Sayori, what are you apologizing for?" with dissolve
    r frown_side "Sí, Sayori, ¿por qué te disculpas?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1832
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_685545f6:

    # s neutral "A week ago, when this whole nonsense began, I called him \"irredeemable filth\"." with dissolve
    s neutral "Hace una semana, cuando esta locura comenzó, lo llamé una \"irredimible escoria\"." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1835
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_e26a6abb:

    # s uniform_folded sleeptalk "For you to go this far to make amends... I never thought you had it in you, Kyou." with dissolve
    s uniform_folded sleeptalk "Que hayas ido tan lejos por enmendar las cosas... Nunca te creí capaz, Kyou." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1836
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_d97ef6f0:

    # s concerned_right "So I am sorry for doubting your sincerity that day, and I take those words back. For what it's worth." with dissolve
    s concerned_right "Así que lamento haber dudado de tu sinceridad aquel día, y me retracto de lo que dije. Si sirve de algo." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1838
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_e7a1b6a6:

    # "That must be the nicest thing anyone's said to me all week, but Sayori turns her attention to the others before I can even thank her for it." with dissolve
    "Eso debe ser lo más amable que alguien me ha dicho en toda la semana, pero Sayori dirige su atención a las otras antes de que pueda agradecérselo." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1839
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_6d480d92:

    # s "Now, I want to be clear to both of you that our roles in this deception we played today are not over." with dissolve
    s "Y ahora, quiero aclararles a ambas que nuestro papel en este engaño aún no termina." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:3938
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_4b2ea6c9:

    # "Nozomi nods solemnly."
    "Nozomi asiente solemnemente."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1843
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_42dc5e56:

    # n sad_closed "Right. We still need to act like we believe what we said back there." with dissolve
    n sad_closed "Cierto. Aún debemos actuar como si creyéramos lo que dijimos allá." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1844
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_5604f741:

    # s uniform "Good. Only the five of us, including Hiroko, know the true story of the \"panty thefts\"." with dissolve
    s uniform "Correcto. Solamente nosotros cinco, Hiroko incluida, sabemos la verdadera historia del \"ladrón de pantaletas\"." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1847
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_2a6ea55e:

    # s concerned "If word got out to the faculty that this scandal was fabricated we could all be in serious trouble, and Kyou's sacrifice will have been for nothing." with dissolve
    s concerned "Si llega a oídos de la facultad que este escándalo fue orquestado, podríamos tener serios problemas, y el sacrificio de Kyou habrá sido en vano." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1848
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_5eca630f:

    # r uniform concerned "Yeah, message received. We got your back on this, Kyou." with dissolve
    r uniform concerned "Seh, mensaje recibido. Te tenemos cubierto, Kyou." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1850
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_f14228ed:

    # s uniform_folded concerned_right "And as for you, Kyou." with dissolve
    s uniform_folded concerned_right "Y en cuanto a ti, Kyou." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1851
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_06acd751:

    # ks neutral "Yeah?"
    ks neutral "¿Sí?"

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1853
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_96837e4d:

    # s sleeptalk "Good luck for the future. I mean it." with dissolve
    s sleeptalk "Buena suerte en el porvenir. Lo digo en serio." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1854
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_5b47e137:

    # s uniform neutral_right "If you need any help preparing for your entrance exams, I may be able to offer some assistance." with dissolve
    s uniform neutral_right "Si necesitas ayuda preparándote para tus exámenes de admisión, podría ofrecerte algo de asistencia." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1855
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_c0e416e1:

    # "I smile at her in thanks. It's a small thing, but winning her respect does feel nice after everything that's happened."
    "Le sonrío en agradecimiento. No es mucho, pero ganarme su respeto se siente bien luego de todo lo que ha pasado."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1858
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_50e46e30:

    # "But as I leave the karaoke place, it's a feeling that quickly dissipates."
    "Pero al salir del karaoke, ese sentimiento tarda poco en disiparse."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1859
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_496cf523:

    # "I can win the respect of those girls all I want. I still need to keep this deception going."
    "Puedo ganarme el respeto de esas chicas todo lo que quiera. Aún debo seguir con la farsa."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1860
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_ee9790be:

    # "I'm still walking alone."
    "Sigo caminando solo."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1867
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_d102837c:

    # "I'm still... alone."
    "Sigo... solo."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1868
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_10c57c81:

    # "Was it even worth it? Right now it's hard to think I made a difference today, and I gave up everything I had left."
    "¿Habrá valido la pena? En este momento es difícil pensar que hice alguna diferencia hoy, y renuncié a todo lo que me quedaba."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1872
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_55579e15:

    # "What's going to happen to Hiroko now? It's maddening that I don't know."
    "¿Qué le pasará ahora a Hiroko? No saberlo me vuelve loco."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1873
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_52615ecb:

    # "... What's even going to happen to me?"
    "... ¿Qué me pasará a mí?"

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1875
translate spanish Day11_Redemption_cf93ed55:

    # "(( AUTHOR'S NOTE - This concludes the current written script. The epilogue currently remains outlined as it was in the previous release. ))"
    "(( NOTA DE LA AUTORA – Esto concluye el guion que hay escrito hasta ahora. El epílogo actualmente sigue en bosquejo, justo como en la actualización anterior. ))"
