    # ks "You told me all the things I could do for this show and you saw me; I just did what what we agreed."
    ks "Me dijiste todas las cosas que podía hacer en el espectáculo y tú me viste; hice solo lo que acordamos."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:3036
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_b9c46c66:

    # ks "None of that stuff should've been dangerous in any way. So why..."
    ks "Nada de eso debió ser peligroso de ninguna manera. Entonces ¿por qué?..."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:3037
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_11f5665a:

    # n side sad_side "It doesn't matter, Kyou." with dissolve
    n side sad_side "Eso no importa, Kyou." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:3038
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_baed8b35:

    # ks "What? What do you mean it doesn't matter?"
    ks "¿Qué? ¿Cómo que no importa?"

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:3039
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_7c70e728:

    # "My question hangs in the air for a moment as Nozomi holds a hand up to touch her formerly-bruised cheek."
    "Mi pregunta queda en el aire por un momento, mientras Nozomi frota con una mano su antes moreteada mejilla."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:3040
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_e3f2cece:

    # n sad_closed "... Nothing's going to change the fact we hurt mom because we wanted to experiment." with dissolve
    n sad_closed "... Nada cambiará el hecho de que le hicimos daño a mamá porque queríamos experimentar." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:3041
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_d51556c2:

    # n sad_side "I wanted to prove we could use your penlight to hypnotize and be hypnotized; to have the most wonderful experience, and be able to do it safely." with dissolve
    n sad_side "Quería probar que podíamos usar la linterna para hipnotizar y ser hipnotizados; para tener una experiencia de lo más maravillosa, y ser capaces de hacerlo seguro." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:3042
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_a3b66420:

    # n sad "We knew it was dangerous. But I still... I still wanted to believe it was possible." with dissolve
    n sad "Sabíamos que era peligroso. Pero aun así... aun así quería creer que era posible." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:3043
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_ea24c16f:

    # n front2 sleeptalk_concerned "And because of that, I hurt myself. I hurt Hiroko. Mom... even you, Kyou." with dissolve
    n front2 sleeptalk_concerned "Y a causa de eso, me hice daño. Le hice daño a Hiroko. A mamá... Incluso a ti, Kyou." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:3044
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_a2dc03be:

    # n cry "All because I wanted to pursue my selfish desires." with dissolve
    n cry "Todo porque quise perseguir mis deseos egoístas." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:3045
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_0135f0e9:

    # ks surprised "Hey, Nozomi... c-come on, you're not selfish."
    ks surprised "Oye, Nozomi... v-vamos, no eres egoísta."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:3046
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_576ea919:

    # "Nozomi starts to cry in front of me. As if this evening could get any worse."
    "Nozomi comienza a llorar delante de mí. Como si esta noche pudiera ponerse peor."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:3047
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_de8887a4:

    # n frightened "Y-yes I am! I wanted a cheap thrill all to myself, and I lied and used the people I love just for a chance at it." with dissolve
    n frightened "¡S-sí lo soy! Quise buscar estas sensaciones fuertes solo para mí, y mentí y usé a la gente que quiero solo por la oportunidad de conseguirlas." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:3048
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_cec92ec0:

    # n concerned "But... b-but I can stop." with dissolve
    n concerned "Pero... p-pero puedo parar." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:3049
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_3c4a7af8:

    # "I wonder for a moment what she means, only I notice her gaze is drawn to my right pants pocket."
    "Me pregunto por un momento a qué se refiere, pero entonces noto su mirada sobre el bolsillo derecho de mi pantalón."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:3053
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_0272c3c2:

    # "The pocket where I keep my penlight."
    "El bolsillo en el que guardo mi linterna."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:3054
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_9eaece2f:

    # n sleeptalk_concerned "We can stop, Kyou." with dissolve
    n sleeptalk_concerned "Podemos parar, Kyou." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:3055
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_699c1357:

    # "Stop our experiments? No. It's obvious from Nozomi's expression she wants more than that."
    "¿Parar con nuestros experimentos? No. Es obvio por la expresión de Nozomi que quiere más que eso."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:3056
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_8e4ee8a4:

    # "... She wants me to stop using the penlight, period."
    "... Quiere que deje de usar la linterna y punto."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:3057
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_5c547186:

    # "Just give up the crowning achievement of my entire life. Hell, the only thing that brought us together."
    "Renunciar al logro más grande de toda mi vida. Vaya, la única cosa que pudo unirnos."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:3060
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_f1be6798:

    # "... I can't bear to see Nozomi in this much pain."
    "... No soporto ver a Nozomi con tanto dolor."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:3062
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_913002d3:

    # "This penlight of mine... I may have built it, but I still don't understand how it does what it does." with dissolve
    "Esta pluma linterna mía... yo la habré fabricado, pero aun así no entiendo cómo hace lo que hace." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:3064
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_6d76f24a:

    # "And as I wrap my fingers around it and try to bend it in two, it seems I'll never understand..."
    "Y al apretarla entre mis dedos, intentando doblarla por la mitad, parece que nunca lo entenderé..."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:3067
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_f9a8138a:

    # "Nozomi wipes her eyes as she watches the penlight visibly bend in my hands. And when I go to click the switch, we see how it fails to light." with dissolve
    "Nozomi se limpia los ojos, viendo la linterna claramente torcida en mis manos. Y cuando presiono el interruptor, veo que no hay ni rastro de luz." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:3068
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_e295e571:

    # "So... that's that, then."
    "Pues... entonces, se acabó."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:3069
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_1105bb37:

    # ks sigh "I guess this means our show's cancelled too, huh."
    ks sigh "Supongo que nuestro espectáculo también queda cancelado."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:3070
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_695bccdb:

    # n side sad_closed "Y... yeah..." with dissolve
    n side sad_closed "S... sí..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:3072
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_63268879:

    # "With our decision made, all that's left for tonight is to finish up downstairs."
    "Habiendo tomado nuestra decisión, ya solo queda atender lo del piso de abajo."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:3081
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_f267a181:

    # n "How are we doing down here?"
    n "¿Cómo les va aquí abajo?"

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:3082
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_0d46e093:

    # "We return to the living room to find Sayori and Hiroko are still waiting for us."
    "Volvemos a la sala y encontramos que Sayori y Hiroko nos siguen esperando."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:3084
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_afc4f1a9:

    # h frown_side "Fine. Was just wondering what you an' Kyou were talking about that you didn't wanna loop me in on." with dissolve
    h frown_side "Bien. Solo me preguntaba de qué estaban hablando Kyou y tú que no me querían contar." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:3085
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_d1749071:

    # n sad_closed "Yeah, sorry. It was a delicate subject." with dissolve
    n sad_closed "Sí, lo siento. Era un tema delicado." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:3086
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_1f839871:

    # "I can't help but chuckle as I notice Hiroko's still holding those loose socks in her fists."
    "No puedo evitar reírme al notar que Hiroko sigue con esos calcetines en sus puños."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:3087
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_b45699eb:

    # ks smile "Hehe, yeah. And you seem a little preoccupied."
    ks smile "Jeje, sí. Y tú pareces un poco ocupada."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:3092
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_29f835bb:

    # n "Kyou, mind your manners in my house!" with dissolve
    n "¡Kyou, cuida tus modales en mi casa!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:3093
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_f4486127:

    # "... Right. Hiroko's not the only one I need to sort out while I'm here."
    "... Cierto. Hiroko no es la única a la que necesito arreglar."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:3063
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_2f2ff332:

    # ks frown "Alright, both of you need to pay attention to me."
    ks frown "Muy bien, ustedes dos, préstenme mucha atención."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:3097
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_e9ae9cd7:

    # "I thought they both might have lost their hypnotic conditioning after I went upstairs. It's pretty clear we've finished our act, after all." with dissolve
    "Creí que ambas habrían perdido su acondicionamiento hipnótico después de que subí las escaleras. Está muy claro que ya terminó el acto, después de todo." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:3098
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_6715885d:

    # "But I guess I should know by now that they won't let go on their own. I really do need to be direct with them."
    "Pero supongo que ya debería saber que no las dejarán ir por su cuenta. Realmente tengo que ser directo con ellas."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:3099
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_0f217fda:

    # ks frown "We're finished for tonight, okay? The show's over."
    ks frown "Ya acabamos por hoy, ¿de acuerdo? El espectáculo terminó."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:3100
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_f423aaae:

    # ks "That means you're no longer hypnotized and everything I said to you in your deep states of relaxation no longer has any affect on your behaviour. Understand?"
    ks "Eso significa que ya no están hipnotizadas y todo lo que les dije cuando estaban en un profundo estado de relajación ya no tiene efecto en su comportamiento. ¿Comprenden?"

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:3102
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_cd08c9c0:

    # h uniform_armup angry "Why're you talking like we're a couple idiots? I know we finished up in..." with dissolve
    h uniform_armup angry "¿Por qué nos hablas como idiotas? Ya sé que terminamos con..." with dissolve

