translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_0d617db9:

    # "We all go silent as Atsuko suddenly returns from the kitchen."
    "Todos caemos en silencio cuando Atsuko repentinamente regresa de la cocina."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:3135
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_3ba9a37f:

    # "I may have rid her of my penlight-assisted hypnosis, but I did nothing for the hurt it apparently caused her. Now that I think about it." with dissolve
    "Puede que la haya librado de la hipnosis hecha con la linterna, pero no hice nada por el dolor que aparentemente le causó, ahora que lo pienso." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:3136
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_5b3fa539:

    # nm sleep "Oh, don't make those faces. I'm okay now." with dissolve
    nm sleep "Oh, no pongan esas caras. Ya estoy bien." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:3137
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_09a92111:

    # nm neutral_side "Seeing Hansuke again after all these years was quite a shock, but I guess... it was a little cathartic, too." with dissolve
    nm neutral_side "Ver a Hansuke de nuevo luego de todos estos años fue un gran impacto, pero supongo que... también un poco catártico." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:3138
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_aba17b7a:

    # nm neutral "I always wanted to yell at that creepy old bastard." with dissolve
    nm neutral "Siempre quise gritarle a ese viejo bastardo." with dissolve

    # game/Kyou 11.rpy:3337
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_d3b2c375:

    # "I still want to know who the fuck this Hansuke guy was. This apparantly famous person that hurt her twenty years ago."
    "Aún quiero saber quién carajos era ese tal Hansuke. Esa persona aparentemente famosa que la lastimó hace veinte años."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:3140
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_764bf69e:

    # "But I guess I know better than to ask right now, so all I can do is bow my head."
    "Pero supongo que será mejor no preguntar ahora mismo, así que no puedo hacer más que inclinar mi cabeza."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:3143
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_423f099f:

    # ks sigh "I'm sorry, Atsuko. I really wanted you to have fun with everyone else."
    ks sigh "Lo siento, Atsuko. De verdad quería que se divirtiera con las demás."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:3144
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_b12e73e5:

    # nm smile "I know, dear. And it was fun while it lasted." with dissolve
    nm smile "Lo sé, cariño. Y fue divertido mientras duró." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:3145
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_af474d00:

    # n sad_closed "It really was... but we're going to do something else for the culture festival." with dissolve
    n sad_closed "Vaya que sí... pero haremos otra cosa para el festival cultural." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:3147
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_c17be9ec:

    # h surprised_side "Wait, seriously?" with dissolve
    h surprised_side "Espera, ¿en serio? " with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:3149
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_3903bf07:

    # nm surprised_side "Oh... I hope that's not on my account." with dissolve
    nm surprised_side "Oh... espero que no sea a causa mía." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:3150
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_90d9df84:

    # n sad_side "No!" with dissolve
    n sad_side "¡No!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:3154
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_527a1d8c:

    # n "W-well, okay it is a bit." with dissolve
    n "B-bueno, un poquito, sí." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:3155
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_4616d6c0:

    # n concerned "And I realized I don't feel comfortable performing hypnosis in front of everyone, s-so..." with dissolve
    n concerned "Y me di cuenta de que no me siento cómoda practicando hipnosis delante de todos, a-así que..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:3156
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_7b452a3e:

    # "She glances towards me as she says it. I guess that's about as truthful as she can be to everyone else right now."
    "Mira en mi dirección al decirlo. Supongo que eso es lo más que puede decir de la verdad en este momento."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:3157
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_f2ee0940:

    # h uniform sad_side "Right? I don't really wanna do all this crap in front of people. Jesus." with dissolve
    h uniform sad_side "¿Verdad? En serio no quiero hacer nada de esto delante de la gente. Dios santo." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:3160
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_49d09560:

    # nm neutral_side "Alright, Nozomi. If that really is how you feel." with dissolve
    nm neutral_side "Muy bien, Nozomi. Si así es como te sientes." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:3161
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_5cf643df:

    # nm "But I don't want you regretting tonight. I'm happy you asked me for help."
    nm "Pero no quiero que te arrepientas de esta noche. Estoy feliz de que me hayas pedido ayuda."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:3163
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_83c8a53c:

    # n "H-huh?" with dissolve
    n "¿E-eh?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:3275
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_cd892787:

    # nm smile_side "Just know I'll support you in everything you do. Okay, hun?" with dissolve
    nm smile_side "Quiero que sepas que te apoyaré en todo lo que hagas. ¿De acuerdo, querida?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:3168
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_cf9875c6:

    # n "Mom, I..."
    n "Mamá, yo..."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:3171
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_1a42186a:

    # n happy "... Okay." with dissolve
    n happy "... De acuerdo." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:3187
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_db294a72:

    # "Kyou thinks she's being way too hasty and is just reacting in the moment."
    "Kyou cree que está actuando muy apresuradamente y solo está reaccionando al momento."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:3188
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_ffd2035c:

    # "Sure it's done some damage to use the penlight, but she has to admit that the added pressure of their hectic school schedule hasn't helped."
    "Claro, usar su linterna ha causado algo de daño, pero tiene que admitir que la presión adicional de su agitado horario de escuela no ha ayudado."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:3189
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_e50330d1:

    # "When things are a little calmer they can try again, surely."
    "Cuando las cosas se hayan calmado un poco, seguro puede volver a intentarlo."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:3191
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_3decc380:

    # "Nozomi insists he break it, and doesn't take Kyou's refusal well at all." with dissolve
    "Nozomi insiste en que la destruya, y no se toma nada bien la negación de Kyou." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:3193
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_08228694:

    # "As she raises her voice, Kyou realises he needs to shut this down now." with dissolve
    "Cuando alza su voz, Kyou se da cuenta de que tiene que hacer algo." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:3195
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_8cec442f:

    # "First, he informs her that their show isn't over, which confuses her for a moment as he reaches for her shoulder..." with dissolve
    "Primero, le informa que su espectáculo no ha terminado, lo cual la confunde por un memento hasta que él pone una mano sobre su hombro..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:3197
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_86ff4338:

    # "... and activates the little sleep trigger he put on all of them during the show." with dissolve
    "... y activa la pequeña ancla de sueño que les puso a todas durante el espectáculo." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:3198
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_cfd85783:

    # "And it works! Nozomi's head slumps forward as her protesting dies on her lips, reduced to nothing more than a sleepy sigh as she drops into trance in spite of herself."
    "¡Y funciona! La cabeza de Nozomi cae hacia adelante y sus protestas perecen en sus labios, reducidas a nada más que un soñoliento suspiro al caer obligada al trance."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:3199
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_d3e95a89:

    # "After all that commotion, both of them realized that Kyou never actually said the show was over earlier; it was only Nozomi who said it was."
    "Después de toda la conmoción, ambos se dan cuenta de que Kyou nunca dijo que el espectáculo había terminado, solo Nozomi lo dijo."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:3202
