    # ks "Shh... it's alright."
    ks "Shh... decuida."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:3245
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_657038f1:

    # "With a gentle motion, I reach down to lift her up in my arms before carrying her carefully to rest on her own bed while I continue to speak to her subconscious mind."
    "Con gentileza, me agacho para levantarla y cargarla cuidadosamente para posarla en su cama, mientras continúo hablándole a su subconsciente."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:3246
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_2f8b8a43:

    # ks "I know you're having doubts, and I know you're scared. But you didn't really mean what you said just now, did you?"
    ks "Sabes que tienes dudas, y sabes que tienes miedo. Pero lo que dijiste hace un momento no era en serio, ¿o sí?"

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:3385
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_e31c1571:

    # n "I..." with dissolve
    n "Lo que..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:3248
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_d907c703:

    # ks "I know you don't want to stop this. And so do you, Nozomi."
    ks "Sé que no quieres parar con esto. Y tú también, Nozomi."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:3388
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_92ae51d8:

    # ks "So I want to tell you it's okay. You don't have to be scared of what happened, or what might happen." with dissolve
    ks "Así que quiero decirte que está bien. No debes tener miedo de lo que ocurra, o lo que pueda ocurrir." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:3250
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_a8cd8f0e:

    # ks "Instead, you can just relax. Let all of those worries and doubts and concerns fall away from your mind..."
    ks "En vez de eso, puedes relajarte. Deja que todas esas preocupaciones y dudas se desvanezcan de tu mente..."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:3251
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_4e0322c0:

    # ks "Let them all go, and let me be scared for both of us."
    ks "Deja que todas se vayan, y déjame cargar con el miedo de ambos."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:3252
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_8a93d582:

    # ks "I'll take care of everything from now on. Okay, Nozomi?"
    ks "Yo me haré cargo de todo. ¿Muy bien, Nozomi?"

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:3253
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_80a27b93:

    # n sleeptalk "Ah..." with dissolve
    n sleeptalk "Ah..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:3254
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_685cba74:

    # "I smile as her expression softens with a calm sigh, while I wipe the tears from her face."
    "Sonrío al ver que su expresión se suaviza con un calmado suspiro, mientras limpio las lágrimas de su rostro."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:3255
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_bbbb2d3b:

    # n "Okay..."
    n "Bien..."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:3397
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_5bf6c191:

    # ks smile "Of course it's okay. So in a moment you're going to wake up again from this wonderful state of trance, ready to continue everything we're doing together." with dissolve
    ks smile "Claro que está bien. Así que en un momento despertarás de este maravilloso estado de trance, lista para continuar con todo lo que estamos haciendo juntos." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:3257
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_16fdf5f1:

    # ks "Ready to awaken and let me worry about all of this in one, two..."
    ks "Despertarás y dejarás que yo me preocupe por todo en uno, dos..."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:3261
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_fe2bf186:

    # ks "Three."
    ks "Tres."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:3262
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_fb240be5:

    # "((AUTHOR'S NOTE: And that's as far as I've gotten on this story path I'm afraid. ))"
    "(( NOTA DE LA AUTORA: Y hasta aquí logré llegar en esta historia, me temo. ))"

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:3263
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_692182fc:

    # "(( Stay tuned for more developments on this in a later update! ))"
    "(( ¡Manténganse en sintonía para mayor desarrollo en una próxima actualización! ))"

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:3408
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_a08c132c_1:

    # "{size=30}TO BE CONTINUED...{/size}"
    "{size=30}CONTINUARÁ...{/size}"

