# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1687
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_cc8a3903:

    # n sad_side "W-well anyway, I thought we could start with you, Hiroko." with dissolve
    n sad_side "B-bueno, en fin, pensé que podríamos empezar hablando de ti, Hiroko." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1690
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_6172a3ba:

    # h "Huh? Me?" with dissolve
    h "¿Eh? ¿De mí?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1691
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_c83775ed:

    # "I find myself leaning in as the pair of them talk."
    "Me inclino ligeramente hacia adelante al oírlas hablar."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1692
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_09dffc89:

    # n happy "Mhm! Are you still feeling good about doing the show with us?" with dissolve
    n happy "¡Mjm! ¿Aún te sientes bien con la idea de hacer el espectáculo con nosotros?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1693
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_a46d0fcc:

    # "Needless to say, I'm rather interested in Hiroko's feelings as well."
    "Sobra decir que también tengo mucho interés en los sentimientos de Hiroko."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1694
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_ca60603c:

    # h uniform_headhold2 "Oh, uhh... yeah, why wouldn't I be?" with dissolve
    h uniform_headhold2 "Oh, eeh... sí, ¿por qué no me sentiría bien?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1695
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_5d2c7c67:

    # "After all, I'm not quite done assessing the results of yesterday's experiment."
    "Después de todo, aún no he terminado de evaluar los resultados del experimento de ayer."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1696
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_ad3b3383:

    # n sad_side "Oh I don't know, it's... well, sometimes people say some weird things when they've just come out of hypnosis." with dissolve
    n sad_side "Oh, no sé, es que... bueno, a veces la gente dice cosas raras cuando acaban de salir del trance." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1697
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_f03cf13b:

    # "I've not had a chance to see if a hypnotic suggestion I made with the penlight can last beyond an hour or more."
    "No he tenido alguna oportunidad de ver si una sugestión posthipnótica hecha con la linterna puede durar más de una hora, o incluso un día."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1700
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_a33f0308:

    # n neutral_side "So I want you to know, if you've had any second thoughts about it, it's okay." with dissolve
    n neutral_side "Así que quiero que sepas que, si cambiaste de opinión, puedes decirnos." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1701
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_9a8a51fa:

    # "Is she still helpless to resist my secret suggestions to her subconscious even now?"
    "¿Aún será incapaz de resistir mi sugestión secreta a su subconsciente incluso ahora?"

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1704
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_0c08479e:

    # h sleeptalk "Man, where's this coming from? You know me; I ain't gonna say shit that I don't mean." with dissolve
    h sleeptalk "¿Caray, por qué tanta duda? Ya me conoces; si digo que quiero hacerlo es porque quiero hacerlo." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1705
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_4a22db14:

    # n smile_side blush "Yeah. Sorry, I just... I guess I'm still a little shocked that you actually liked it, that's all." with dissolve
    n smile_side blush "Sí. Lo siento, es que... supongo que sigo un poco sorprendida de que sí te gustara, es todo." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1711
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_c3bbacd4:

    # "I hear Hiroko let out a slight chuckle as a smile spreads across her lips." with dissolve
    "Escucho a Hiroko soltar una ligera risa, y una sonrisa se extiende por sus labios." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1712
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_3eb93f0a:

    # h "You and me both. That was some freaky shit you guys pulled, but it was fun."
    h "Ya somos dos. Esa mierda sí estuvo rara, pero fue divertido."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1713
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_ed7ca92d:

    # "Oh yes, those whispered words of mine are still living comfortably inside her head."
    "Oh, sí, mis susurros siguen viviendo cómodamente en su cabeza."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1714
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_61ff8294:

    # h surprised_side "Like, man, I couldn't stop thinking about it last night. Just thinking about how trippy that all was when Kyou shined the light in my eyes..." with dissolve
    h surprised_side "O sea, caray, no pude dejar de pensar en eso anoche. Solo pensar en cómo se sintió cuando Kyou me puso esa luz en los ojos." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1715
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_3710bf23:

    # "So I think I can safely conclude that my experiment has been a complete success."
    "Creo que puedo concluir con seguridad que mi experimento ha sido un completo éxito."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1718
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_e418cf60:

    # s uniform_folded sleeptalk "Well, this is quite the turnaround from yesterday, isn't it." with dissolve
    s uniform_folded sleeptalk "Vaya, esto sí que es un giro dado de un día para otro, ¿no?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1719
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_542d8d49:

    # "However, it seems Nozomi and I aren't the only ones assessing the situation with Hiroko..."
    "Sin embargo, parece que Nozomi y yo no somos los únicos evaluando la situación con Hiroko..."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1725
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_dd881c31:

    # s sleeptalk "I am napping. And I am also listening." with dissolve
    s sleeptalk "Estoy durmiendo una siesta. Y también estoy escuchando." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1726
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_a257dee6:

    # s "So would you mind telling me what happened?"
    s "Entonces, ¿podrían compartirme lo sucedido?"

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1729
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_882ed647:

    # h uniform_headhold2 rolleyes "Man, why do you even care? Don't you think this's a waste of time anyway?" with dissolve
    h uniform_headhold2 rolleyes "Caray, ¿a poco te importa? ¿Qué tú no crees que es una pérdida de tiempo?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1730
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_fd616cfc:

    # s happy "Perhaps I can be convinced otherwise with the telling." with dissolve
    s happy "Tal vez pueda ser convencida de lo contrario si me cuentan la historia." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1731
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_e676a879:

    # h sleeptalk "Ugh, whatevs. So yeah, Kyou did some trick with a light and put me to sleep with it." with dissolve
    h sleeptalk "Ay, como sea. Pues bueno, Kyou hizo un truco con una luz y me puso a dormir." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1751
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_68a7b10b_1:

    # h "Ain't you supposed to be napping?" with dissolve
    h "¿Qué tú no te ibas a echar una siesta?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1764
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_c915a351:

    # s uniform_folded "From what little I learned, I do understand that it requires a willingness on the part of the hypnotized." with dissolve
    s uniform_folded "Por lo poco que aprendí, entiendo que es requerida la voluntad del hipnotizado." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1773
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_334a14f7:

    # h uniform_armup surprised_side "That's just it! I figured I'd just half-ass it, y'know? Play along and stuff, s'all I was gonna do." with dissolve
    h uniform_armup surprised_side "¡Esa es la cosa! Pensaba solo hacer lo mínimo. Medio seguir el juego y así. Solo eso tenía que hacer." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1795
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_93d7bf5b_1:

    # h uniform_headhold2 sleeptalk novein noblush "But... fuck, man, I dunno. The instant that light hit my eyes it's like some freak switch flipped in my brain an' I forgot all about faking it." with dissolve
    h uniform_headhold2 sleeptalk novein noblush "Pero... mierda, no sé. En cuanto la luz tocó mis ojos es como si un interruptor se hubiera movido en mi cerebro y me olvidé de fingir." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1800
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_d2e54cd1:

    # h rolleyes "Like, duh? You really thought I was gonna take you serious?" with dissolve
    h rolleyes "Pues, ¿daaa? ¿De verdad creíste que te tomaría en serio?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1801
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_b7a29781:

    # h sad "I was so ready to call bullshit on the whole thing, but next thing I know I'm waking up back in that chair and... damn, dude, you really got me back there." with dissolve
    h sad "Estaba lista para demostrarte que era una pendejada, y lo siguiente que recuerdo es despertar en esa silla y... diablos, viejo, sí te salió bien." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1802
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_089ddc46:

    # h sleeptalk "An' ever since then I keep going back to it, like, over and over, almost like I'm trying to hypno myself." with dissolve
    h sleeptalk "Y desde entonces sigo pensando en ello, o sea, una y otra vez, casi como si tratara de hipnotizarme a mí misma." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1803
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_e4f049ec:

    # h sleepy "Really didn't think I'd... um, enjoy it so much." with dissolve
    h sleepy "De verdad no pensé que lo... em, disfrutaría tanto." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1805
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_20a2ec5a:

    # "Sayori taps her cheek thoughtfully." with dissolve
    "Sayori golpetea su mejilla con un dedo, pensativamente." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1807
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_9672c5bf:

    # s concerned "I wonder if in the moment you felt more comfortable with the arrangement than you first realized." with dissolve
    s concerned "Me pregunto si en el momento te sentiste más cómoda con la situación de lo que pensabas." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1808
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_5c22fa88:

    # s sleeptalk "Perhaps after your frustration with the examinations, the temptation to simply zone out for a while became a compelling one, regardless of the circumstances." with dissolve
    s sleeptalk "Quizás tras tu frustración con los exámenes, la tentación de despejar tu mente por un rato resultó atractiva, sin importar las circunstancias." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1809
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_46a07390:

    # s smile "Not to mention, you were not alone with our would-be hypnotist. I imagine Nozomi's presence was a comforting one." with dissolve
    s smile "Sin mencionar que no estuviste sola con nuestro presunto hipnotista. Imagino que la presencia de Nozomi fue reconfortante." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1810
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_c3e8a93a:

    # h uniform confused_side "Shit, Sayori, I just don't know any more." with dissolve
    h uniform confused_side "Mierda, Sayori, ya ni yo sé." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1811
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_26e84ec0:

    # h sleep "All I know for sure is I wanna go again..." with dissolve
    h sleep "Lo único que sé con certeza es que quiero hacerlo otra vez..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1812
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_c5ae06e5:

    # s sleep "Hmm..." with dissolve
    s sleep "Mmm..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1813
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_a66af051:

    # "With a sudden shake of her head, Hiroko then turns back to Nozomi and me."
    "Hiroko sacude repentinamente la cabeza, luego voltea a vernos de nuevo a Nozomi y a mí."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1814
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_74f40251:

    # h frown "So c'mon, what're we all doing for this show thingy? That's why we're here, right?" with dissolve
    h frown "¿Y bien? ¿Qué vamos a hacer en el espectáculo este? Para eso estamos aquí, ¿no?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1816
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_87bf8a24:

    # n sad "Uh, right..." with dissolve
    n sad "Eh, cierto..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1856
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_3a0edc4c:

    # h "Huh? Why the hell do we need volunteers for?" with dissolve
    h "¿Eh? ¿Para qué diablos necesitamos voluntarios?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1857
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_2259342d:

    # n sad_side "You saw what Satoshi did, right? Picking out people from the audience is all a part of the show; that's how it's done." with dissolve
    n sad_side "Tú viste lo que hizo Satoshi, ¿verdad? Elegir a gente de la audiencia es parte del acto; así es como se hace." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1858
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_d1443280:

    # "Hiroko simply scoffs and rolls her eyes."
    "Hiroko simplemente se mofa y voltea los ojos."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1859
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_f9dba53d:

    # h rolleyes "Look, Nozo, you said it yourself; we got twenty minutes to do this thing. Why do you wanna waste time with a bunch of randos?" with dissolve
    h rolleyes "Mira, Nozo, tú misma lo dijiste: tenemos veinte minutos para la cosa esta. ¿Por qué quieres perder tiempo con un montón de extraños?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1860
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_17fd8ebc:

    # "Seems Hiroko has her own ideas for our routine. How interesting."
    "Parece que Hiroko tiene sus propias ideas para nuestra rutina. Qué interesante."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1861
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_98508f5f:

    # h frown "'Sides, his show weren't all that; why're you trying to do the same thing as Mister Pocketwatch anyway?" with dissolve
    h frown "Además, su acto no estuvo tan bueno; ¿por qué intentas hacer lo mismo que el señor Reloj de Bolsillo?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1862
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_496cbb28:

    # "I know we wanted a range of hypnotic subjects to test what my penlight could do, and this was the perfect opportunity, but even so..."
    "Sé que queríamos ampliar el rango de sujetos hipnóticos para probar lo que la linterna puede hacer, y esta era la oportunidad perfecta, sin embargo..."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1863
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_b2f0e7fa:

    # ks smirk "Wait, Hiroko, you're not suggesting..."
    ks smirk "Espera, Hiroko, no estarás sugiriendo..."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1864
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_30c8594b:

    # "I like where this is going."
    "Me gusta a dónde va esto."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1865
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_0ebdd003:

    # h uniform_armup angry "Jus' do all that stuff with me! You know I'm good for it." with dissolve
    h uniform_armup angry "¡Solo háganlo todo conmigo! Ya saben que soy buena para eso." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1866
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_f1e6cd6f:

    # n surprised_side "Y-you... you're saying you want to do everything?" with dissolve
    n surprised_side "¿D-dices... dices que quieres hacer todo?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1867
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_398faf47:

    # h irritated "FUCK yeah! I mean, what're you gonna do with these guys in twenty anyway? What if you get a buncha fakers like this dude's saying?" with dissolve
    h irritated "¡Claro que SÍ! Digo, ¿qué van a hacer con esos pendejos en veinte minutos? ¿Qué tal si les tocan puros idiotas que finjan como Kyou dijo?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1868
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_f47757c5:

    # n sad_closed "W-well... that's why I said we should pick them out before the show." with dissolve
    n sad_closed "B-bueno... por eso decía que deberíamos elegirlos con anterioridad." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1869
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_d92a50fa:

    # h uniform_headhold2 frown_side "Who do you think's gonna do it for us, Nozo? And even if they did, d'ya reckon they'll be on my level when they're up there in front of folks?" with dissolve
    h uniform_headhold2 frown_side "¿Quién crees que va a hacer esto por nosotros, Nozo? Y aunque alguien aceptara, ¿crees que estará a mi nivel cuando suba al escenario?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1871
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_5045816a:

    # h frown "Face it, you guys can do way cooler stuff if it was just me. None of that lame-ass \"cluck like a chicken\" shit." with dissolve
    h frown "Acéptenlo, pueden hacer cosas mucho más geniales si soy solo yo. Nada de esas pendejadas de \"hacer ruidos de gallina\"." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1872
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_d6417adc:

    # n rolleyes "Oh, come on." with dissolve
    n rolleyes "Oh, vamos." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1873
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_77b5fb3c:

    # h uniform_armup angry_side "For real, though! Just lemme practice an' I'll make some jaws drop, you'll see!" with dissolve
    h uniform_armup angry_side "¡Pero en serio! ¡Solo déjenme practicar y los dejaré a todos boquiabiertos! ¡Ya verán!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1875
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Zombie_9c48c350:

    # n sad_side "Do you even know what you're saying now? You're taking on a lot of pressure for just a culture fest show." with dissolve
