    # ks "One, two... beginning to stir, letting your eyes open wide and..."
    ks "Uno, dos... comienzas a moverte, abriendo bien los ojos y..."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1409
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_81d90efb:

    # "I let out a shuddered sigh, my breath catching as I dread the consequence of what I'm about to do..."
    "Dejo salir un estremecido suspiro, con falta de aliento por el temor a las consecuencias de lo que estoy a punto de hacer..."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1410
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_73d67bc0:

    # ks "T-Three! Awaken now, Nozomi."
    ks "¡T-tres! Despierta ahora, Nozomi."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1411
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_c6690c32:

    # n sleepy "..." with dissolve
    n sleepy "..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1412
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_727c0845:

    # "Nozomi's eyes slowly come back into focus as I watch the emotions play out on her face."
    "Los ojos de Nozomi recuperan lentamente el enfoque, y veo las emociones desenvolverse en su rostro."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1414
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_c3bc19cf:

    # "Her mouth starts to hang open in shocked silence, with the memories of her experience surely flashing before her now fully-conscious mind." with dissolve
    "Su boca se abre en conmocionado silencio, mientras que los recuerdos de su experiencia seguramente están siendo reproducidos ante su mente ahora consciente." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1416
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_576901f1:

    # "Then her lower lip begins to tremble as her eyes dart to register me, standing over her vulnerable, now quivering body." with dissolve
    "Su labio inferior empieza a tiritar cuando sus ojos captan mi presencia, al estar de pie frente a su vulnerable y ahora temblante cuerpo." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1467
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_e436310a:

    # n "H-hrrrrr..."
    n "Cj... ñññññ..."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1418
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_5c3db850:

    # "I shouldn't be here. I can't see her like this any more."
    "No debería estar aquí. No puedo seguir viéndola así."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1419
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_4e07e4f5:

    # ks sad "Y-yeah, I'm... I'm gonna give you some privacy."
    ks sad "S-sí, voy... voy a darte algo de privacidad."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1420
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_8b784479:

    # "So I turn around and I start to walk away, only stopping briefly at the doorframe to utter meaninglessly:"
    "Así que me doy la vuelta y comienzo a alejarme, solo deteniéndome brevemente en el marco de la puerta para decir algo que tal vez signifique poco."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1421
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_3d9e01c3:

    # ks sigh "I'll be in my room if you want to... talk about it. Or whatever."
    ks sigh "Estaré en mi habitación si quieres... hablar al respecto. O cualquier cosa."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1424
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_52ca2ad4:

    # "What else could I even say?"
    "¿Qué más podría decir?"

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1426
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_b37aef0f:

    # "Nozomi wanted me to push her. If I hadn't gone as far as I did, would she have ever been satisfied?"
    "Nozomi quería que la llevara al límite. Si no hubiera ido así de lejos, ¿habría estado satisfecha?"

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1427
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_621c7f9d:

    # "But even if she truly had no limits in the end, shouldn't I have had my own?"
    "Pero incluso si ella, en última instancia, de verdad no tenía límites, ¿no debería haberlos tenido yo?"

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1428
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_e83e4df3:

    # "I never had to do that to her. I didn't have to make that choice."
    "No tenía por qué hacerle eso. No tenía por qué tomar esa decisión."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1429
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_6155ff26:

    # "No matter what, I'm her hypnotist. I'm still responsible for what happened in there."
    "Sin importar qué, yo soy su hipnotista. Sigo siendo responsable por lo que pasó ahí."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1430
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_02e8fc28:

    # "I'm responsible for everything, so..."
    "Soy responsable de todo, así que..."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1433
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_dc4ea75b:

    # "... Only a quiet knocking on my door snaps me back to the real world."
    "... Solo un suave golpeteo en mi puerta logra traerme de vuelta al mundo real."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1435
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_ebf7e280:

    # n "{size=16}K-... Kyou?{/size}"
    n "{size=16}¿K-... Kyou?{/size}"

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1436
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_7f2ba9f2:

    # ks sigh "... Yeah, I'm here."
    ks sigh "... Sí, aquí estoy."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1440
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_dd07f472:

    # "She didn't just leave?"
    "¿No se fue sin más?"

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1441
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_288fcea9:

    # n "Hey..."
    n "Hola..."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1442
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_295df5e6:

    # ks sad "... Hey."
    ks sad "... Hola."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1443
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_7b226a1b:

    # "I wouldn't have blamed her if she ran out of my house screaming."
    "No la habría culpado si hubiera salido corriendo de mi casa gritando."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1444
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_ddbabfd6:

    # "But here she is, standing pensively in the doorway as we regard each other with pained stares."
    "Pero hela aquí, parada pensativamente en la puerta mientras intercambiamos una acongojada mirada."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1445
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_40c32057:

    # ks "Are you... okay?"
    ks "¿Estás... bien?"

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1447
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_6d3f3637:

    # "Nozomi doesn't answer. She only bows her head as she slowly pads over to my side and sits with me on the bed."
    "Nozomi no responde. Solo agacha la cabeza mientras camina lentamente hacia mí, y se sienta a mi lado en la cama."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1448
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_96da6753:

    # "It takes another long moment before she finally begins to speak."
    "No es hasta luego de un largo momento que finalmente comienza a hablar."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1449
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_60e36c84:

    # n sleeptalk "N-no, Kyou... I don't think I'm okay." with dissolve
    n sleeptalk "N-no, Kyou... No creo estar bien." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1450
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_8e372f84:

    # ks "... I'm sorry."
    ks "... Lo siento."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1451
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_630e51d2:

    # n side sad_closed "Why are you apologizing?" with dissolve
    n side sad_closed "¿Por qué te disculpas?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1452
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_12f570c3:

    # ks confused "Why? I went too far, didn't I?"
    ks confused "¿Que por qué? Fui muy lejos, ¿no?"

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1453
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_cd05c512:

    # n sad_side "Yeah... you did." with dissolve
    n sad_side "Sí... es cierto." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1454
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_0fe828bf:

    # "She trembles beside me as she averts her eyes from me and holds a hand to her temple."
    "Tiembla junto a mí, apartando la mirada con una mano en su sien."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1455
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_5cccabd4:

    # n sad_closed "B-but what did I think was going to happen?" with dissolve
    n sad_closed "P-pero ¿qué pensaba yo que iba a pasar?" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1456
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_14e00912:

    # n "I wanted you to dominate my mind; to go all the way. Explore my fantasies to the fullest."
    n "Quería que dominaras mi mente; que fueras hasta las últimas consecuencias. Explorar mis fantasías al máximo."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1457
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_e5a75022:

    # n sad "It's what I wanted. But also... n-not." with dissolve
    n sad "Es lo que quería. Pero a la vez... n-no." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1458
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_3c1c5cfe:

    # n "I just thought, there still had to be a limit, right? There had to be something I wouldn't do; something I'd be able to resist, no matter how deep I was into it."
    n "Pero pensé que tendría que haber algún límite, ¿verdad? Tenía que haber algo que no fuera a hacer; algo que hubiera sido capaz de resistir, sin importar lo profundo que estuviera."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1459
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_82ca7cd8:

    # n front2 sleep_concerned "All you did was show me that when it comes down to it, I don't have limits. I don't have a bottom." with dissolve
    n front2 sleep_concerned "Lo único que hiciste fue mostrarme que, a la hora de la verdad, no tengo límites. No tengo fondo." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1460
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_66d17bd9:

    # n scared "Y-you showed me... t-that I can't trust myself to be hypnotized. I can't trust myself to separate fantasy from... f-from reality and just... j-just..." with dissolve
    n scared "M-me mostraste... qu-que no puedo confiar en mí misma para ser hipnotizada. No puedo confiar en que podré distinguir la fantasía de... d-de la realidad y pues... p-pues..." with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1461
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_5f17af77:

    # n cry "Hrrr... O-ohh god, I'm so messed up!" with dissolve
    n cry "Ñññ... ¡Ooh, Dios, estoy muy mal!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1462
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_0fdb5d0c:

    # "I look down at her as she hunches over, choking down sobs."
    "Observo cómo se inclina hacia adelante, ahogándose entre sollozos."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1463
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_14a35a1f:

    # "And all I can do is place an arm around her in some futile attempt to offer her comfort."
    "Y lo único que puedo hacer es arroparla con mi brazo en un fútil intento de reconfortarla."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1464
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_a7e20fd6:

    # n frightened "I'm SO messed up!" with dissolve
    n frightened "¡Estoy MUY mal!" with dissolve

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1465
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_4858325c:

    # "Like, Christ, what do I even say to her?"
    "Es que, Dios, ¿qué podría decirle ahora?"

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1466
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_280e588f:

    # ks "I... it's alright, Nozomi. We don't have to do this anymore."
    ks "T-... tranquila, Nozomi. No tenemos que seguir haciendo esto."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1467
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_fa62d38b:

    # n "W-we won't. I won't..."
    n "N-no lo haremos. No seguiremos..."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1468
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_38a94d05:

    # n "I'll never put my mind in danger again, I swear it!"
    n "¡No volveré a poner mi mente en peligro jamás, lo juro!"

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1469
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_f8d8049d:

    # "I can only nod grimly. That this would be the end of our adventures in hypnosis was practically a given."
    "No puedo más que asentir con melancolía. Estaba claro que este iba a ser el fin de nuestras aventuras con la hipnosis."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1470
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_b721e3f2:

    # "The idea of hypnotizing her again no longer excites me. Not after what it's done to her."
    "La idea de hipnotizarla otra vez ya no me causa ninguna ansia. No después de lo que le ha hecho."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1471
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_07518e14:

    # "If this is what hypnosis can do a person?"
    "¿Es esto lo que la hipnosis puede hacerle a una persona?"

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1472
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_e4b809d1:

    # "I don't think I could ever do this to someone again. Especially not to Nozomi."
    "No creo poder volverle a hacer esto a alguien. Mucho menos a Nozomi."

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1474
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_3f7f21b2:

    # "But does that mean this is the end of... of us?"
    "Pero ¿significa eso que este es el fin de... de nosotros?"

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1475
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_0fa879fa:

    # "(( AUTHOR'S NOTE: Okay, I'm gonna leave things here for now so I can push this release out to all of you and prepare a CG for the previous scene. ))"
    "(( NOTA DE LA AUTORA: Muy bien, voy a dejarlo aquí por ahora para poder mostrarles esta actualización y preparar un CG para la escena anterior. ))"

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1476
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_935b6928:

    # "(( In the next update I want to wrap this up with a short epilogue to show how these two end up, along with some new artwork. ))"
    "(( En la próxima actualización, quiero cerrar con un breve epílogo mostrando qué será de estos dos, junto con el nuevo arte. ))"

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1477
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_001588d8:

    # "(( So please look forward to that~ ))"
    "(( Así que, por favor, espérenlo con ansias. ))"

# game/Kyou 11.rpy:1478
translate spanish Day11_Con_Kyou_Nozomi_Trance_9bce48c1:

    # "(( {size=32}TO BE CONTINUED...{/size}))"
    "(( {size=32}CONTINUARÁ...{/size} ))"

translate spanish strings:

    # game/Kyou 11.rpy:1214
    old "I'll order her to stop breathing"
    new "Le ordenaré que deje de respirar"

    # game/Kyou 11.rpy:1214
    old "I need to put a stop to this"
    new "Debo ponerle un alto a esto"
